1
00:00:01,902 --> 00:00:04,836
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON</i> THE PRETENDER.

2
00:00:04,904 --> 00:00:07,205
ENOUGH!
WE DON'T WANT HIM DEAD.

3
00:00:07,274 --> 00:00:08,806
[ Tires Screeching ]

4
00:00:08,875 --> 00:00:11,576
<i> NICE TO MEET YOU, JAROD.</i>
<i> I'M ZOE.</i>

5
00:00:13,213 --> 00:00:16,081
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>I WANT TO STAY WITH YOU.</i>
<i> [ Zoe ] I KNOW.</i>

6
00:00:16,149 --> 00:00:20,251
<i>BUT YOU CAN'T STAY, CAN YOU?</i>
<i>I CAN SEE IT IN YOUR EYES.</i>

7
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:23,188
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>EDNA RAINES KNOWS THINGS</i>
<i>ABOUT YOUR MOTHER, MISS PARKER.</i>

8
00:00:23,257 --> 00:00:26,024
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT YOUR MOTHER AND MIRAGE.

9
00:00:26,093 --> 00:00:27,725
IT COULD BE A MATTER
OF LIFE AND DEATH.

10
00:00:27,794 --> 00:00:29,927
<i>[ Sydney ]</i>
<i>EDNA RAINES IS DEAD.</i>

11
00:00:29,996 --> 00:00:32,430
SHE KNEW ALL THE SECRETS,
ESPECIALLY ABOUT
THE MIRAGE PROJECT.

12
00:00:32,499 --> 00:00:35,033
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>JAROD'S E-MAIL</i>
<i>SAID TO KEEP DIGGING.</i>

13
00:00:35,102 --> 00:00:37,736
IT'S YOUR MOTHER'S GRAVE.
MISS PARKER, YOUR MOTHER--
SHE'S NOT HERE.

14
00:00:37,805 --> 00:00:40,038
THEN WHERE THE HELL IS SHE?

15
00:00:46,413 --> 00:00:48,880
<i>OH, COME ON.</i>
<i>EVERYBODY'S BEEN ON</i>
<i>AT LEAST ONE VACATION.</i>

16
00:00:48,949 --> 00:00:51,617
I SWEAR, ZOE,
I'VE NEVER BEEN
ON VACATION.

17
00:00:51,685 --> 00:00:54,385
NOT EVEN, UH,
MOUNT RUSHMORE?

18
00:00:55,823 --> 00:00:58,257
- THE ALAMO?
- MM-MMM.

19
00:00:58,325 --> 00:01:02,027
WHAT ABOUT NIAGARA FALLS?

20
00:01:02,096 --> 00:01:04,896
I DEFINITELY WOULD HAVE
REMEMBERED THAT.

21
00:01:04,965 --> 00:01:10,368
WAIT, I DID EAT AT A "STOOKEY'S"
OFF OF I-65 ONCE.
DOES THAT COUNT?

22
00:01:10,437 --> 00:01:13,905
"STUCKEY'S." ONLY IF
YOU BOUGHT THE PECAN LOG.

23
00:01:13,974 --> 00:01:17,910
WHAT'S A PECAN LOG?
OH, YOU REALLY HAVE NEVER
HAD A VACATION, HAVE YOU?

24
00:01:17,978 --> 00:01:21,847
WHO NEEDS A VACATION...
WHEN I HAVE YOU?

25
00:01:26,453 --> 00:01:29,054
YOU SWEAR TO ME
YOU'RE IN TOTAL REMISSION?

26
00:01:29,123 --> 00:01:33,825
YEAH. I PROBABLY PISSED OFF
A FEW H.M.O.'s,
BUT WHAT THE HELL?

27
00:01:35,696 --> 00:01:37,629
ZOE--
HEY.

28
00:01:37,698 --> 00:01:40,399
YOU'RE NOT GOING
ALL MUSHY ON ME, ARE YOU?

29
00:01:40,468 --> 00:01:42,701
<i>[ Ringing ]</i>
<i>[ Electronic Voice ]</i>
<i>YOU HAVE A VIDEO PHONE CALL.</i>

30
00:01:42,770 --> 00:01:45,003
THAT'S MY VIDEO PHONE.

31
00:01:45,072 --> 00:01:48,807
UM, I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.
OKAY.

32
00:01:52,179 --> 00:01:55,146
<i>[ Ringing Continues ]</i>

33
00:01:55,215 --> 00:01:59,183
- HELLO, SON.
- OH, MY GOD! DAD!

34
00:01:59,252 --> 00:02:02,019
<i>I'VE BEEN SEARCHING FOR YOU</i>
<i>FOR OVER A YEAR.</i>
<i>WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?</i>

35
00:02:02,088 --> 00:02:04,989
I KNOW.
THE BOY AND I HAD TO GO
UNDERGROUND FOR A WHILE.

36
00:02:05,058 --> 00:02:07,191
WE KEPT SEARCHING FOR YOU TOO,
BUT WITH NO LUCK,

37
00:02:07,260 --> 00:02:09,628
UNTIL AN ANONYMOUS TIP
CAME MY WAY.

38
00:02:09,696 --> 00:02:13,031
I WAS ABLE
TO UNSCRAMBLE YOUR PASSWORD,
WHICH GOT ME INTO YOU HERE.

39
00:02:13,099 --> 00:02:16,301
- THEN YOU'RE BOTH OKAY?
- THANK GOD THE BOY AND I
ARE BOTH WELL.

40
00:02:16,369 --> 00:02:19,872
THE BOY?
HE'S SORT OF LIKE
MY BROTHER. I'LL--

41
00:02:19,940 --> 00:02:25,009
I'LL EXPLAIN IT
TO YOU SOMETIME.
DAD, THIS IS ZOE.

42
00:02:25,078 --> 00:02:29,180
ZOE, THIS IS MY DAD.
JAROD'S BEEN PRETTY
DAMN WORRIED ABOUT YOU, SIR.

43
00:02:29,249 --> 00:02:32,216
HE'S CUTE.
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

44
00:02:32,285 --> 00:02:34,552
WHEN CAN I SEE YOU?

45
00:02:34,621 --> 00:02:37,722
WE HAVE TO BE CAREFUL.
I DON'T TRUST THE SECURITY
OF THIS LINE,

46
00:02:37,791 --> 00:02:39,691
SO I'LL MAKE IT QUICK.

47
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:42,127
JAROD, I FOUND EMILY.

48
00:02:42,195 --> 00:02:44,729
I FOUND YOUR SISTER.

49
00:02:44,798 --> 00:02:48,033
WHAT? HOW? WHERE IS SHE?

50
00:02:48,101 --> 00:02:51,403
SHE'S A REPORTER AT
THE<i> PHILADELPHIA EXAMINER.</i>
FOR SECURITY'S SAKE,

51
00:02:51,472 --> 00:02:55,340
I'VE LEFT VITAL INFORMATION
ABOUT HER WHEREABOUTS
ON YOUR SECURED E-MAIL.

52
00:02:55,408 --> 00:02:58,476
SHE TOLD ME THAT RECENTLY,
SHE WAS VERY CLOSE
TO FINDING YOU.

53
00:02:58,545 --> 00:03:01,580
SHE CRIED WHEN I TOLD HER
I KNEW HOW TO REACH YOU.

54
00:03:01,648 --> 00:03:03,815
I THINK
YOU SHOULD GO TO HER.

55
00:03:03,884 --> 00:03:06,184
WILL YOU BRING HER BACK
TO ME, JAROD?
<i>YES!</i>

56
00:03:06,253 --> 00:03:10,922
- YES, OF COURSE I WILL.
- GOOD LUCK, SON.
KEEP ME POSTED.

57
00:03:13,594 --> 00:03:16,194
MY-- I FOUND MY DAD.
UM--

58
00:03:16,262 --> 00:03:19,097
MY-- I--
WE'VE BEEN LOOKING FOR
MY SISTER FOR SO LONG,

59
00:03:19,165 --> 00:03:21,099
AND NOW I FOUND HER,
AND I CAN, UH--

60
00:03:21,167 --> 00:03:24,503
UM-- WHAT ABOUT OUR TRIP?

61
00:03:24,571 --> 00:03:27,706
IT CAN WAIT.
WE'LL HAVE TIME.

62
00:03:27,774 --> 00:03:32,110
AND IF I HAVE ANY SAY
IN THE MATTER, LOTS OF IT.

63
00:03:32,178 --> 00:03:34,445
YOU'RE NOT GETTIN'
ALL MUSHY ON ME,
ARE YOU?

64
00:03:34,515 --> 00:03:36,681
GO FIND YOUR SISTER.

65
00:03:58,438 --> 00:04:00,405
<i>[ Man ]</i>
<i>SOMEBODY CALL 911!</i>

66
00:04:00,474 --> 00:04:02,574
<i>[ Woman ]</i>
<i>SHE'S IN THE ALLEY!</i>

67
00:04:02,643 --> 00:04:05,043
WHAT HAPPENED?
A REPORTER WAS ATTACKED.

68
00:04:05,111 --> 00:04:07,612
- THEY SAY SHE WAS THROWN
OUT OF THAT WINDOW.
-<i> A REPORTER?</i>

69
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,981
AN EMILY SOMETHING.

70
00:04:12,152 --> 00:04:16,788
EMILY? EMILY!

71
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:21,460
EMILY? EMILY?

72
00:04:21,528 --> 00:04:23,895
PLEASE HELP ME.
THAT'S WHAT I'M HERE TO DO.

73
00:04:23,964 --> 00:04:26,898
I'M GOING TO HELP YOU.
I'M JAROD.
I'M YOUR BROTHER.

74
00:04:26,966 --> 00:04:29,934
JAROD.
STAY WITH ME.
STAY WITH ME.

75
00:04:31,171 --> 00:04:33,438
[ Gasps, Coughs ]
EMILY? EMILY?

76
00:04:33,507 --> 00:04:36,274
SOMEBODY CALL AN AMBULANCE!

77
00:04:36,342 --> 00:04:39,477
<i>[ Man Narrating ]</i>
<i>THERE ARE PRETENDERS AMONG US.</i>

78
00:04:39,546 --> 00:04:41,479
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>I WAS TAKEN FROM MY FAMILY.</i>

79
00:04:41,548 --> 00:04:45,116
<i>THIRTY-SIX HOURS AND HE'S</i>
<i>ALREADY DEMONSTRATING MORE</i>
<i>TALENT THAN ANY OF OUR OTHERS.</i>

80
00:04:45,185 --> 00:04:48,586
<i>HOW MANY PEOPLE DIED</i>
<i>BECAUSE OF WHAT I THOUGHT UP?</i>

81
00:04:48,655 --> 00:04:52,090
SINCE I BROKE OUT,
I'VE SPENT EVERY MOMENT
SEARCHING FOR MY PAST.

82
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:54,359
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>HE'S A PRETENDER--</i>

83
00:04:54,428 --> 00:04:57,195
<i>A GENIUS WHO CAN BECOME</i>
<i>ANYONE THAT HE WANTS TO BE.</i>

84
00:04:57,264 --> 00:04:59,998
-<i> THE CENTRE WANTS HIM ALIVE.</i>
- PREFERABLY.

85
00:05:00,067 --> 00:05:03,000
<i>- [ Miss Parker ] HE DEFENDS</i>
<i>  THE WEAK AND ABUSED.</i>
<i>- [ Jarod ] LIFE'S A GIFT.</i>

86
00:05:14,782 --> 00:05:17,248
-<i> YOU A DOCTOR?</i>
- I AM TODAY.

87
00:05:25,058 --> 00:05:29,761
PUPILS ARE UNRESPONSIVE.
RESPIRATION IS SHALLOW AT 40.
PULSE IS WEAK AND THREADY.

88
00:05:29,829 --> 00:05:32,998
PROBABLE CLOSED HEAD INJURY
WITH INTERNAL BLEEDING
AND MULTIPLE FRACTURES.

89
00:05:33,066 --> 00:05:36,134
KEEP HER HEAD STABILIZED.
START AN I.V. DRIP
AND RUN A C.B.C.

90
00:05:36,203 --> 00:05:39,237
PAGE RADIOLOGY.
WE NEED AN ABDOMINAL
AND HEAD CAT SCAN, STAT.

91
00:05:39,305 --> 00:05:42,440
- WHO INITIATED C.P.R.?
- I DID.

92
00:05:42,509 --> 00:05:44,843
YOUR ACTIONS
MAY HAVE SAVED HER LIFE.
ARE YOU A DOCTOR?

93
00:05:44,912 --> 00:05:46,845
NO.

94
00:05:46,914 --> 00:05:48,847
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>I'M WITH THE F.B.I.</i>

95
00:05:48,915 --> 00:05:52,884
THE VICTIM IS SOMEONE WE'VE HAD
OUR EYE ON FOR SOMETIME NOW.
WHY?

96
00:05:52,953 --> 00:05:56,487
LET'S JUST SAY THAT A FEW
OF HER JOURNALISTIC CHOICES
HAVE STRUCK A NERVE IN D.C.

97
00:05:56,556 --> 00:05:58,823
THE VICTIM'S OFFICE
IS IN HERE.

98
00:06:08,569 --> 00:06:10,935
<i>NAME'S DETECTIVE BROOKINS.</i>
<i>CALL ME STAN.</i>

99
00:06:12,005 --> 00:06:14,038
AGENT JAROD CURTIS.

100
00:06:14,107 --> 00:06:16,041
TELL ME WHAT YOU KNOW,
THE WHOLE STORY.

101
00:06:16,109 --> 00:06:18,477
WELL, THE VICTIM CAME TO
THE OFFICE EARLY THIS MORNING.

102
00:06:18,545 --> 00:06:22,046
SO EARLY, IT WAS THE NIGHT SHIFT
JANITOR THAT PROBABLY
SAVED HER LIFE BY WALKING IN.

103
00:06:22,115 --> 00:06:24,782
ANYWAY, FROM WHAT I CAN TELL,
THE WOMAN WAS AMBUSHED HERE,

104
00:06:24,851 --> 00:06:28,853
THEN THROWN OUT THIS WINDOW
TWO STORIES TO THE PAVEMENT.

105
00:06:31,525 --> 00:06:36,161
ANY DESCRIPTION?
WHITE MALE, 35-ISH,
AVERAGE BUILD, DARK SUIT.

106
00:06:36,230 --> 00:06:38,363
<i>GOT THE SKETCH ARTIST</i>
<i>WORKIN' ON IT NOW.</i>

107
00:06:38,432 --> 00:06:41,466
I WANT ALL OF HER FILES
BOXED AND SEALED
AND SENT TO YOUR PRECINCT.

108
00:06:41,535 --> 00:06:44,136
<i> AND I'M ALSO GONNA NEED</i>
<i> AN OFFICE FOR A FEW DAYS.</i>

109
00:06:48,107 --> 00:06:51,542
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>WELL, IT'S ABOUT TIME</i>
<i>YOU GOT BACK, LYLE.</i>

110
00:06:51,611 --> 00:06:56,615
<i> SO, WHAT'S THE FLAVOR</i>
<i> OF THE DAY, LITTLE BROTHER?</i>

111
00:06:56,683 --> 00:06:58,649
MAIL-ORDER MAMAS
FROM MALAYSIA?

112
00:07:00,253 --> 00:07:02,954
OR CANNIBAL QUICHE
FROM THE KALAHARI?

113
00:07:03,022 --> 00:07:06,857
IF YOU'RE HERE TO TALK
WITH OUR FATHER, HE'S GONE.
WELL, THEN FIND HIM.

114
00:07:06,926 --> 00:07:12,763
[ Chuckles ]
POUNDING BOILERMAKERS IS HARDLY
THE BREAKFAST OF CHAMPIONS.

115
00:07:12,833 --> 00:07:15,834
THIS ISN'T ABOUT YOU.
I'M SORRY.

116
00:07:15,902 --> 00:07:17,936
OKAY, NOW I KNOW YOU'RE SLOSHED.

117
00:07:18,004 --> 00:07:19,937
<i>WHAT'S GOING ON, PARKER?</i>

118
00:07:20,006 --> 00:07:24,709
<i> [ Sighs ]</i>
<i> IT'S--</i>

119
00:07:24,778 --> 00:07:27,445
IT'S ABOUT OUR MOTHER.

120
00:07:28,915 --> 00:07:31,549
SHE'S GONE.

121
00:07:31,618 --> 00:07:34,385
OUR MOTHER'S BEEN DEAD
A LONG TIME.
<i> NO.</i>

122
00:07:34,454 --> 00:07:38,456
I MEAN, SHE'S NOT THERE.
I MEAN, HER--

123
00:07:39,893 --> 00:07:43,961
<i>SHE'S NOT THERE?</i>
<i>WHAT DO YOU MEAN</i>
<i>SHE'S NOT THERE, PARKER?</i>

124
00:07:44,030 --> 00:07:45,696
<i>PARKER?</i>

125
00:07:48,935 --> 00:07:50,868
YOU WOULDN'T UNDERSTAND ANYWAY.

126
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:57,709
- BUT I WANNA KNOW.
- BET YOU DO.

127
00:08:06,452 --> 00:08:08,954
[ Electronic Female Voice ]
MESSAGE VOICE BOX 04.
RECORD.

128
00:08:09,022 --> 00:08:11,489
<i>[ Beeps ]</i>
IT'S ME.

129
00:08:11,558 --> 00:08:15,060
I'VE GOT A BAD FEELING
MISS PARKER KNOWS ABOUT
CATHERINE'S EMPTY GRAVE.

130
00:08:15,128 --> 00:08:18,563
<i>[ Sydney ]</i>
<i>YOU BELIEVE SOMEONE STOLE</i>
<i>YOUR MOTHER'S BODY?</i>

131
00:08:18,632 --> 00:08:23,034
EXCEPT FOR THIS
SCOTCH-INDUCED EARTHQUAKE
RATTLING BETWEEN MY EARS,

132
00:08:23,103 --> 00:08:25,971
I'M NOT SURE EXACTLY
WHAT TO BELIEVE ANYMORE.

133
00:08:26,039 --> 00:08:29,407
<i> LET'S FACE IT, SYDNEY.</i>
<i> CATHERINE PARKER'S BODY</i>
<i> BEING GONE...</i>

134
00:08:29,475 --> 00:08:33,244
FITS IN WITH ALL THE OTHER
BIZARRE HAPPENINGS AROUND HERE.

135
00:08:33,313 --> 00:08:36,714
THE REAPPEARANCE OF EDNA RAINES
WHO, AFTER 30 YEARS,
EVERYONE THOUGHT WAS DEAD.

136
00:08:36,783 --> 00:08:42,353
AND WHO NOW REALLY IS DEAD,
THANKS TO THE BALD BUTCHER
SHE CALLED "HUBBY."

137
00:08:42,422 --> 00:08:45,490
THE MURDER OF THAT
HARMLESS CLERK LEONARD
DOWN IN SL 26...

138
00:08:45,559 --> 00:08:48,093
BECAUSE HE JUST HAPPENED
TO SEE THE WRONG MEMO.

139
00:08:48,161 --> 00:08:51,796
AND NOW, CATHERINE PARKER'S
EMPTY GRAVE. THAT'S A LOT
OF STRANGE COINCIDENCES.

140
00:08:51,865 --> 00:08:54,332
NO. NOT COINCIDENCE.
MIRAGE.

141
00:08:54,401 --> 00:08:57,636
MIRAGE?
YOU MEAN WHAT EDNA RAINES
TOLD YOU BEFORE SHE DIED?

142
00:08:57,704 --> 00:09:01,106
WHAT WAS ON BOTH OF THOSE MEMOS,
THE ONE I FOUND
ON LYLE'S DESK...

143
00:09:01,174 --> 00:09:02,540
AND THE ONE
THAT KILLED THAT CLERK.

144
00:09:02,608 --> 00:09:04,709
WELL, ODDITIES, YES,

145
00:09:04,777 --> 00:09:06,777
BUT STATUS QUO
HERE AT THE CENTRE.

146
00:09:06,846 --> 00:09:08,779
I NEVER THOUGHT
I'D HEAR YOU SAY...

147
00:09:08,849 --> 00:09:11,883
"MURDER IS BUSINESS AS USUAL,"
SYD.

148
00:09:11,951 --> 00:09:14,919
ALL I'M SAYING IS,
AT TIMES...

149
00:09:14,988 --> 00:09:17,355
IT IS BEST
TO LET SOME THINGS GO.

150
00:09:17,424 --> 00:09:20,224
MY MOTHER'S GRAVE
IS EMPTY, SYDNEY.

151
00:09:20,293 --> 00:09:24,762
MAYBE, JUST MAYBE,
SHE HAD OTHER WISHES
THAT YOU DIDN'T KNOW ABOUT.

152
00:09:24,831 --> 00:09:27,932
<i> FOR HER BURIAL, I MEAN.</i>
<i> PEOPLE SOMETIMES</i>
<i> MAKE CHOICES...</i>

153
00:09:28,001 --> 00:09:30,635
THAT ARE DIFFICULT
TO EXPLAIN.

154
00:09:30,703 --> 00:09:33,204
NO.

155
00:09:34,707 --> 00:09:37,141
THIS IS ONE BIG FISH
I'M REELING IN.

156
00:09:38,644 --> 00:09:42,313
BROOTS, OUR BEST EVIDENCE--
WE FOLLOW THE BODY.

157
00:09:42,382 --> 00:09:47,652
<i>IN THIS CASE, MY MOTHER'S.</i>
<i>WE START WITH</i>
<i>THE AUTOPSY RECORDS.</i>

158
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,821
PARKER?

159
00:09:50,991 --> 00:09:53,325
WHY WON'T YOU
LET GO OF THIS?

160
00:09:55,762 --> 00:10:00,899
BECAUSE SOMETHING INSIDE ME
IS TELLING ME TO DO THIS.

161
00:10:02,269 --> 00:10:04,201
AND I'M LISTENING.

162
00:10:16,349 --> 00:10:18,449
HER CONDITION IS ONLY FAIR,
AGENT CURTIS.

163
00:10:18,517 --> 00:10:21,118
<i> SO PLEASE MINIMIZE</i>
<i> YOUR TIME WITH HER.</i>
<i>I WILL. THANK YOU.</i>

164
00:10:37,504 --> 00:10:40,271
EM?

165
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:42,473
IT'S YOUR BROTHER,

166
00:10:42,542 --> 00:10:44,609
JAROD.

167
00:10:47,247 --> 00:10:52,116
I WAS TOO LATE THIS MORNING.
I'M SORRY.

168
00:10:52,185 --> 00:10:55,720
<i>BUT I'LL NEVER BE LATE AGAIN.</i>

169
00:10:55,788 --> 00:10:58,355
I PROMISE YOU.

170
00:11:01,361 --> 00:11:03,294
<i>[ Lyle ]</i>
<i>HOW GOES THE WORLD TOUR?</i>

171
00:11:03,363 --> 00:11:05,230
IN DEFERENCE
TO WINSTON CHURCHILL,

172
00:11:05,298 --> 00:11:07,332
OR WHOEVER
THE HELL SAID IT,

173
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:09,467
"THE SUN NEVER SETS
ON THE CENTRE."

174
00:11:09,536 --> 00:11:11,903
AND I'M MAKING SURE
IT NEVER SETS
ON THE PARKERS EITHER.

175
00:11:11,971 --> 00:11:14,472
-<i> [ Elevator Bell Dings ]</i>
-<i> GLAD TO HEAR IT.</i>

176
00:11:14,541 --> 00:11:16,674
SINCE WHEN IS RAINES
HOSTING TRIUMVIRATE PERSONNEL?

177
00:11:16,743 --> 00:11:20,578
HE'LL BE A BLIP ON OUR RADAR
AS LONG AS EVERYTHING
GOES WELL WITH MIRAGE.

178
00:11:20,646 --> 00:11:22,613
UNFORTUNATELY,
WE'VE GOT COMPANY THERE.

179
00:11:22,682 --> 00:11:25,649
<i>I'VE ALL BUT CONFIRMED</i>
<i>THAT SIS IS ON THAT SAME TRACK.</i>

180
00:11:25,718 --> 00:11:27,651
AH, DAMN.
OH, IT'S NOTHING.

181
00:11:27,721 --> 00:11:29,687
SHE'S WAY BEHIND THE CURVE.
I'LL MAKE SURE SHE STAYS THERE.

182
00:11:29,756 --> 00:11:31,956
I DON'T WANT HER KNOWING
FOR HER OWN GOOD.

183
00:11:32,024 --> 00:11:35,793
HELL, IF SHE KNEW THE TRUTH,
SHE'D ONLY WISH SHE DIDN'T.

184
00:11:39,599 --> 00:11:41,199
OKAY.
<i>[ Crunch ]</i>

185
00:11:41,268 --> 00:11:43,201
GOD! WHAT'D I JUST STEP IN?
I DON'T KNOW.

186
00:11:43,270 --> 00:11:45,670
BUT IF YOU HURRY,
YOU CAN STILL CATCH IT.
EW!

187
00:11:45,738 --> 00:11:49,507
<i>[ Sydney ] I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU</i>
<i>ACTUALLY FOUND CATHERINE</i>
<i>PARKER'S AUTOPSY FILES, BROOTS.</i>

188
00:11:49,576 --> 00:11:52,043
WELL, I HAVEN'T FOUND IT YET.
BUT, ACCORDING TO BUZZIE,

189
00:11:52,112 --> 00:11:54,211
THE ONLY WAY TO DOWNLOAD
A VISUAL ARCHIVE
IN THE SUBLEVEL...

190
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:57,281
<i> IS TO TAP DIRECTLY</i>
<i> INTO THE SUBLEVEL'S</i>
<i> MAINFRAME TERMINALS.</i>

191
00:11:57,350 --> 00:12:00,051
- WHO THE HELL IS BUZZIE?
- MY PAL DOWN IN COMMUNICATIONS.

192
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:01,986
YOU KNOW THE OLD GUY
WITH THE HEARING AIDS?

193
00:12:02,054 --> 00:12:04,189
HE'S ALWAYS GRIPING
ABOUT THE CONSTANT RINGING
IN HIS EARS.

194
00:12:04,257 --> 00:12:07,358
- I'VE GOT THAT PROBLEM MYSELF.
- GET THIS.

195
00:12:07,427 --> 00:12:10,028
YOU KNOW THE RUMOR
THAT J.F.K. WAS KEPT ALIVE
AS A VEGETABLE SOMEWHERE?

196
00:12:10,096 --> 00:12:12,029
BUZZIE CLAIMS IT WAS
RIGHT HERE IN SL 18.

197
00:12:12,098 --> 00:12:16,701
<i>YEAH, RIGHT NEXT DOOR</i>
<i>TO THE ALIEN CORPSES</i>
<i>NIXON SHOWED JACKIE GLEASON.</i>

198
00:12:16,770 --> 00:12:20,004
THAT WAS HERE TOO?
<i>[ Sydney ]</i>
<i>HEY!</i>

199
00:12:20,073 --> 00:12:22,774
THIS IS ROOM 12.
THIS IS IT.

200
00:12:30,450 --> 00:12:33,684
<i>[ Broots ]</i>
<i>WOW. THIS IS THE ROOM WHERE</i>
<i>THEY DID YOUR MOTHER'S AUTOPSY.</i>

201
00:12:39,292 --> 00:12:42,727
THIS SHOULDN'T TAKE LONG.
<i>[ Zipper Unzipping ]</i>

202
00:12:52,639 --> 00:12:54,639
SYDNEY?

203
00:13:06,052 --> 00:13:08,953
PARKER, YOU OKAY?
FINE, SYD.

204
00:13:11,123 --> 00:13:14,258
I GOT IT.
[ Raines ] THIS BEGINS
THE VISUAL DATA ARCHIVE...

205
00:13:14,327 --> 00:13:18,096
TO BE KNOWN AS
NUMBER 566773.

206
00:13:18,164 --> 00:13:20,397
THE AUTOPSY OF
CATHERINE ELAINE PARKER.

207
00:13:20,466 --> 00:13:22,533
<i>DATE AND TIME TO FOLLOW.</i>

208
00:13:22,602 --> 00:13:25,670
<i>DR. WILLIAM RAINES, M.E.</i>

209
00:13:25,738 --> 00:13:27,672
VERSATILE GUY, THAT RAINES.

210
00:13:27,740 --> 00:13:30,475
BEATS 'EM, BURSTS THEM,
SLICES AND DICES.

211
00:13:30,543 --> 00:13:33,644
<i>[ Raines ]</i>
<i>INITIAL FINDINGS INDICATE...</i>

212
00:13:33,713 --> 00:13:36,748
A SINGLE GUNSHOT WOUND
INTO THE CRANIAL REGION
AS CAUSE OF DEATH.

213
00:13:36,816 --> 00:13:39,550
ANGLE AND FORCE
OF THE HEAD WOUND...

214
00:13:39,619 --> 00:13:44,888
<i>STRONGLY INDICATE THE GUNSHOT</i>
<i>WAS SELF-INFLICTED.</i>

215
00:13:47,227 --> 00:13:51,062
- [ Drill Whirring ]
- LET'S JUST SKIP
TO THE END, BROOTS.

216
00:13:51,130 --> 00:13:53,665
OH, GOD. WE'VE HEARD
ALL THESE LIES BEFORE.

217
00:13:53,733 --> 00:13:56,233
I JUST NEED TO SEE
WHERE THE BODY GOES.

218
00:13:57,938 --> 00:14:01,272
BOX THE BODY FOR TRANSPORT
PER THE FAMILY WISHES.

219
00:14:05,778 --> 00:14:10,948
ON A PERSONAL NOTE, I WOULD
SIMPLY LIKE TO GO ON RECORD TO
EXPRESS MY HEARTFELT REMORSE,

220
00:14:11,017 --> 00:14:14,685
<i>AND TO SAY THAT THIS IS</i>
<i> AND WILL ALWAYS BE...</i>

221
00:14:14,754 --> 00:14:17,388
<i>A TRAGIC DEATH IN</i>
<i>THE ANNALS OF THE CENTRE,</i>

222
00:14:17,457 --> 00:14:22,292
<i> THE LIKES OF WHICH I HOPE</i>
<i> NEVER TO ENCOUNTER AGAIN.</i>

223
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:26,297
<i> SO, WHAT NOW?</i>

224
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:30,801
WE DO A LITTLE EXPLORATORY
SURGERY OF OUR OWN,

225
00:14:30,870 --> 00:14:35,272
SEE JUST HOW REMORSEFUL
DR. DEATH REALLY IS.

226
00:14:35,341 --> 00:14:38,642
<i>[ Man ]</i>
<i>I'M AS SORRY AS I CAN BE</i>
<i>ABOUT THE ATTACK ON EMILY.</i>

227
00:14:38,711 --> 00:14:41,846
I WISH ALL MY TENANTS
WERE LIKE HER.

228
00:14:41,915 --> 00:14:45,649
I SORT OF CONNECTED
WITH HER RIGHT OFF--

229
00:14:45,718 --> 00:14:48,052
HER LOOKIN' FOR HER FAMILY,

230
00:14:48,121 --> 00:14:50,154
ME NOT EVER KNOWING
MY FATHER AND MOTHER.

231
00:14:50,223 --> 00:14:53,191
I'M SORRY.

232
00:14:55,395 --> 00:15:00,831
SHE WAS SO CLOSE TO CHANGING
ALL THAT FOR HERSELF.

233
00:15:00,901 --> 00:15:03,834
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
WELL, SHE WAS HOT ON
THE TRAIL OF HER BROTHER.

234
00:15:06,473 --> 00:15:09,073
<i>SHE'D TEAR UP EVERY TIME</i>
<i>SHE TALKED ABOUT IT.</i>

235
00:15:09,142 --> 00:15:13,711
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
THAT YOU SAW MY--
UH, THE VICTIM?

236
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:17,148
UM, MUST HAVE BEEN
A COUPLE OF NIGHTS AGO.

237
00:15:17,216 --> 00:15:21,819
TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH,
SHE SEEMED A LITTLE TENSE.

238
00:15:21,888 --> 00:15:26,658
SAID SOMETHING ABOUT BEING, UH,
CLOSE TO A BIG DISCOVERY.

239
00:15:26,727 --> 00:15:28,693
THE BROTHER THAT
SHE WAS LOOKING FOR?

240
00:15:28,761 --> 00:15:31,229
I-I DON'T THINK SO.

241
00:15:31,297 --> 00:15:35,333
THIS WAS SOMETHING
DISTURBING TO HER.
IT WASN'T A HAPPY DISCOVERY.

242
00:15:45,478 --> 00:15:47,412
<i>DID YOU FIND SOMETHING?</i>

243
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:50,548
I'M NOT SURE. UH,
THANK YOU FOR YOUR TIME,

244
00:15:50,617 --> 00:15:53,184
BUT I'D LIKE TO LOOK AROUND
FOR A LITTLE BIT.

245
00:15:53,253 --> 00:15:55,186
SURE. HEY,
YOU SAVED ME A TRIP.

246
00:15:55,255 --> 00:15:59,590
I WAS ABOUT TO GO INTO TOWN AND
TELL THE POLICE ABOUT THIS GUY
THAT WAS HANGING AROUND HERE.

247
00:15:59,659 --> 00:16:02,793
<i>IT-IT WAS THE SAME GUY</i>
<i>FROM THE POLICE SKETCH</i>
<i>IN THE EVENING PAPER.</i>

248
00:16:02,862 --> 00:16:06,764
I-I CAN'T BELIEVE THEY LEFT OUT
THE MOST IMPORTANT PART
OF THE DESCRIPTION.

249
00:16:06,833 --> 00:16:08,399
WHAT'S THAT?

250
00:16:08,468 --> 00:16:11,869
THE FACT THAT-- WELL,
THE GUY WAS MISSING A THUMB.

251
00:16:24,351 --> 00:16:27,252
<i>[ Women Laughing ]</i>
<i>[ Lyle ]</i>
<i>I'VE NEVER EVEN MET YOU.</i>

252
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:29,687
WHO SAID ANYTHING
ABOUT BREAKFAST?

253
00:16:31,991 --> 00:16:34,392
<i> MR. LYLE?</i>

254
00:16:34,461 --> 00:16:36,527
<i>SOMETHING TELLS ME YOU HAVEN'T</i>
<i>READ THE MORNING'S PAPER.</i>

255
00:16:41,234 --> 00:16:44,601
<i>YOU TRY TO KILL WITH KINDNESS,</i>
<i>AND THIS IS WHAT HAPPENS.</i>

256
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:47,038
PUT A TEAM TOGETHER.
WE'RE GOIN' BACK
TO PHILLY A.S.A.P.

257
00:16:47,106 --> 00:16:49,107
RIGHT.

258
00:16:58,852 --> 00:17:01,786
ALLOW ME.

259
00:17:01,855 --> 00:17:04,455
I'M NOT GOING
TO SUBLEVEL 18.

260
00:17:04,523 --> 00:17:08,026
OH. BUT YOU SHOULD.

261
00:17:08,094 --> 00:17:11,462
IT'S A REGULAR
"FREAKS-R-US" DOWN THERE.
YOU KNOW THE HISTORY.

262
00:17:11,531 --> 00:17:16,133
<i> J.F.K., DEAD MARTIANS.</i>
<i> THE ROOM WHERE YOU DID</i>
<i> MY MOTHER'S AUTOPSY.</i>

263
00:17:20,039 --> 00:17:23,408
IT'S GONNA BE A BITCH
GETTIN' THAT TANK
UP AND DOWN THE STAIRS.

264
00:17:23,476 --> 00:17:26,610
IT'S COMMON KNOWLEDGE
I PERFORMED
YOUR MOTHER'S AUTOPSY.

265
00:17:26,679 --> 00:17:30,748
BUT...
IS IT COMMON KNOWLEDGE...

266
00:17:30,817 --> 00:17:34,485
<i>THAT MY MOTHER'S BODY</i>
<i>ISN'T IN HER GRAVE?</i>

267
00:17:34,553 --> 00:17:36,788
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

268
00:17:36,857 --> 00:17:41,825
WHAT THE HELL DID YOU DO
WITH HER BODY, YOU GHOUL?

269
00:17:41,894 --> 00:17:45,930
WHAT ANY RESPONSIBLE
MEDICAL EXAMINER
WOULD HAVE DONE--

270
00:17:45,998 --> 00:17:49,334
HONOR THE WISHES
OF THE DECEASED.

271
00:17:49,402 --> 00:17:52,603
IF YOU HAVE A PROBLEM WITH THAT,
TAKE IT UP WITH HER,

272
00:17:52,671 --> 00:17:55,306
BECAUSE THIS DISCUSSION
IS OVER.

273
00:18:02,248 --> 00:18:05,650
MISS PARKER,
YOU TOLD HIM ABOUT
YOUR MOTHER'S EMPTY GRAVE?

274
00:18:05,718 --> 00:18:07,652
HE'S GONNA--
HE COULD-- HE COULD--

275
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:09,653
HE COULD LEAD US
RIGHT TO THE ANSWER.

276
00:18:09,722 --> 00:18:11,655
<i>[ Broots ]</i>
<i>YOU TOLD HIM ON PURPOSE.</i>

277
00:18:11,725 --> 00:18:14,425
<i>THAT FISH I SAID</i>
<i>I'D BE REELING IN--</i>
<i>I JUST BAITED THE HOOK.</i>

278
00:18:14,493 --> 00:18:17,528
NOW WE TROLL.

279
00:18:17,597 --> 00:18:20,832
- YOU WITH US, SYD?
-<i> [ Elevator Bell Dings ]</i>

280
00:19:01,641 --> 00:19:04,208
<i>[ Woman ]</i>
<i>I'M SORRY, AGENT CURTIS,</i>

281
00:19:04,276 --> 00:19:07,011
<i>BUT I CANNOT IN GOOD CONSCIENCE</i>
<i>ALLOW THE VICTIM</i>
<i>TO BE TRANSFERRED.</i>

282
00:19:07,080 --> 00:19:11,049
HOW WOULD YOUR CONSCIENCE FEEL
WHEN THEY PUT YOU IN JAIL FOR
VIOLATION OF A FEDERAL ORDER?

283
00:19:11,117 --> 00:19:13,851
THAT ORDER IS WORTHLESS
IN MY EYES.
I HAVE SEEN HER CHARTS.

284
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:16,887
HER EDEMA LEVELS
ARE BACK TO NORMAL,
AS WELL AS HER VITAL SIGNS.

285
00:19:16,956 --> 00:19:19,890
- THE ANSWER'S STILL NO.
- WHOEVER TRIED TO KILL HER
KNOWS HE FAILED...

286
00:19:19,959 --> 00:19:23,595
<i> AND HE WILL BE BACK</i>
<i> TO FINISH THE JOB,</i>
<i> I GUARANTEE YOU THAT.</i>

287
00:19:23,663 --> 00:19:27,331
RELEASING HER TO THE NEXT OF KIN
WOULD BE MY ONLY OPTION HERE.
AND CORRECT ME IF I'M WRONG,

288
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:29,566
BUT SO FAR,
NONE HAVE TURNED UP.

289
00:19:29,636 --> 00:19:32,236
<i> UNTIL NOW.</i>
<i> I'M EMILY'S FATHER,</i>

290
00:19:32,305 --> 00:19:34,371
AND I THINK YOU SHOULD GIVE
THE AGENT HERE WHAT HE WANTS.

291
00:19:40,446 --> 00:19:43,314
I'LL PREP HER
FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE.

292
00:19:45,351 --> 00:19:47,885
IT'S SO GOOD TO SEE YOU.
HOW IS SHE?

293
00:19:47,953 --> 00:19:49,686
- SHE'S GOING TO BE OKAY.
- GREAT.

294
00:19:49,755 --> 00:19:51,689
<i> [ Tires Screeching ]</i>

295
00:19:53,026 --> 00:19:55,459
CHECK OVER THERE.
WILLIE, STAIRS.

296
00:19:55,528 --> 00:19:57,528
YOU, FOLLOW ME.

297
00:20:02,035 --> 00:20:04,468
- HOW MANY WERE THERE?
- FOUR.

298
00:20:08,674 --> 00:20:11,075
GO! GO!

299
00:20:17,216 --> 00:20:19,783
238.

300
00:20:22,322 --> 00:20:25,056
DAMN! WHERE DID SHE GO?

301
00:20:25,125 --> 00:20:27,725
- RELEASED.
SHE JUST WENT DOWNSTAIRS.
- TAKE THE STAIRS.

302
00:20:35,634 --> 00:20:38,302
THAT AMBULANCE OVER THERE
IS MINE.

303
00:20:41,174 --> 00:20:43,107
I KNOW A PLACE
THAT WE CAN BE SAFE.

304
00:20:43,176 --> 00:20:45,143
YOU DRIVE.

305
00:21:02,395 --> 00:21:04,995
GOOD WAY TO GET
YOURSELF KILLED, PAL.
OUT OF MY WAY.

306
00:21:05,064 --> 00:21:07,865
- SEE THIS WOMAN
COME THIS WAY ANYWHERE?
-<i> NOPE. NEVER SEEN HER.</i>

307
00:21:15,342 --> 00:21:18,509
<i>[ Siren Wailing ]</i>

308
00:21:23,082 --> 00:21:25,649
DAMN!

309
00:21:25,718 --> 00:21:28,285
<i> I WANNA THANK YOU,</i>
<i> SISTER MARY, FOR EVERYTHING</i>
<i> YOU'VE DONE FOR US.</i>

310
00:21:28,354 --> 00:21:30,488
AFTER ALL YOU'VE DONE
FOR OUR PARISH, JAROD,

311
00:21:30,556 --> 00:21:32,490
YOU JUST STAY
AS LONG AS YOU WANT.
<i>[ Bells Tolling ]</i>

312
00:21:32,558 --> 00:21:35,159
AND WE'LL TAKE
VERY GOOD CARE OF EMILY.

313
00:21:54,713 --> 00:21:56,814
NOTHING.

314
00:21:56,882 --> 00:22:00,251
NO LUCK, HUH?
IT'S LIKE
HE DOESN'T EXIST.

315
00:22:00,320 --> 00:22:03,387
WELL, WHOEVER THIS GUY IS,
EMILY'S BEEN TRACKING HIM
FOR A WHILE.

316
00:22:03,456 --> 00:22:06,023
HERE, LET ME GIVE YOU
A HAND WITH THE NOTES.

317
00:22:11,831 --> 00:22:14,998
"MISPLACED
PERSONALITY DISORDER."
"MAN WITH NO NAME."

318
00:22:15,067 --> 00:22:18,102
"TALKS TO VOICES."
"ENIGMA."

319
00:22:18,171 --> 00:22:20,837
MAYBE IT'S A STORY
SHE'S BEEN WORKING ON.

320
00:22:23,309 --> 00:22:27,512
OR A LIFELONG MYSTERY
SHE'S BEEN TRYING TO SOLVE.

321
00:22:27,580 --> 00:22:29,747
SHE THOUGHT THIS GUY
MIGHT HAVE BEEN YOU.

322
00:22:31,184 --> 00:22:34,118
SHE'S BEEN SEARCHING,
JUST LIKE ME.

323
00:22:34,187 --> 00:22:37,254
JUST LIKE... WE ALL HAVE.

324
00:22:41,994 --> 00:22:45,196
WHY WOULD THE CENTRE
WANT TO MURDER HER?

325
00:22:45,264 --> 00:22:47,531
AND HOW DOES HE FIT IN?

326
00:22:54,139 --> 00:22:56,073
<i>[ Broots ]</i>
<i>BOY, YOU PUT THE WORM ON,</i>

327
00:22:56,141 --> 00:22:58,075
<i>AND HE TOOK IT</i>
<i>HOOK, LINE AND SINKER.</i>

328
00:23:05,985 --> 00:23:08,118
<i>MAN.</i>

329
00:23:08,187 --> 00:23:11,355
BUT I NEVER PEGGED RAINES
FOR THE RUSTIC TYPE.

330
00:23:11,424 --> 00:23:15,058
IN THE MIDDLE OF NOWHERE,
YOU CAN'T HEAR ANYONE SCREAM.

331
00:23:19,365 --> 00:23:21,298
I NEED TO GET TO THAT FIRE.

332
00:23:32,078 --> 00:23:34,211
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>ANYTHING, BROOTS?</i>

333
00:23:36,148 --> 00:23:38,749
LOOKS LIKE
A RAINES TIME CAPSULE.

334
00:23:38,818 --> 00:23:43,754
EVERYTHING FROM
OLD MORTGAGE PAPERS TO
HIS KID'S KINDERGARTEN ARTWORK.

335
00:23:43,823 --> 00:23:45,756
MOVE OVER, MONET.

336
00:23:45,825 --> 00:23:48,659
LOOKS LIKE "ETHAN."
HIS SON?

337
00:23:48,727 --> 00:23:53,196
I'VE TRIED NOT TO FIRE
TOO MANY SYNAPSES REMEMBERING
THINGS ABOUT THE RAINES FAMILY.

338
00:23:53,265 --> 00:23:56,333
YOU THINK RAINES
USED TO LIVE HERE?

339
00:23:56,402 --> 00:23:58,502
WELL, WE USED TO VISIT
HIS HOUSE OCCASIONALLY,

340
00:23:58,571 --> 00:24:00,504
BUT IT WAS ON
THE OTHER SIDE OF TOWN.

341
00:24:00,573 --> 00:24:04,708
MAYBE HE USED THIS PLACE
AS SOME KIND OF PERSONAL
STORAGE DEPOT.

342
00:24:04,777 --> 00:24:07,678
YEAH. WELL, NO OFFENSE
AGAINST HIS KID'S ARTWORK,

343
00:24:07,747 --> 00:24:10,314
BUT THIS IS STARTING TO FEEL
LIKE A DEAD-END TRIP
DOWN MEMORY LANE.

344
00:24:11,784 --> 00:24:13,717
MISS PARKER?

345
00:24:13,786 --> 00:24:16,219
I THINK ANOTHER STREET
JUST OPENED UP.

346
00:24:23,128 --> 00:24:25,395
HUH.
ST. CHRISTOPHER MEDAL.

347
00:24:30,103 --> 00:24:32,603
MISS PARKER, LOOK.

348
00:24:41,247 --> 00:24:43,046
<i>[ Emily Moans ]</i>

349
00:24:45,918 --> 00:24:49,820
EMILY? EMILY?

350
00:24:54,560 --> 00:24:57,061
HI.

351
00:24:58,598 --> 00:25:02,399
IT'S ME, EM.
IT'S YOUR BROTHER.

352
00:25:03,936 --> 00:25:06,337
JAROD?
DAD'S HERE TOO.

353
00:25:09,842 --> 00:25:12,877
WE'RE ALL TOGETHER NOW.

354
00:25:13,980 --> 00:25:15,912
[ Mutters ]

355
00:25:15,981 --> 00:25:19,750
TAKE YOUR TIME.
TAKE YOUR TIME.
WHAT IS IT YOU WANNA TELL US?

356
00:25:21,287 --> 00:25:24,254
<i> I FOUND THIS PICTURE</i>
<i> IN YOUR RESEARCH FILES.</i>

357
00:25:24,323 --> 00:25:27,357
<i> YOU THOUGHT HE WAS ME,</i>
<i> DIDN'T YOU?</i>
<i> WHO IS HE?</i>

358
00:25:27,426 --> 00:25:29,960
ETHAN.

359
00:25:30,028 --> 00:25:34,965
- ETHAN?
- HE HEARS THE VOICES. TALKS--

360
00:25:35,034 --> 00:25:38,903
HE TALKS TO THE VOICES.
I READ THAT IN YOUR NOTEBOOK.
WHAT VOICES, EMILY?

361
00:25:38,971 --> 00:25:42,239
<i> HEY, I THINK</i>
<i> SHE SHOULD REST. COME ON.</i>

362
00:25:42,308 --> 00:25:44,308
OKAY.

363
00:25:51,283 --> 00:25:53,317
NUGENESIS.

364
00:25:53,385 --> 00:25:55,652
NUGENESIS?
MY GOD.

365
00:25:55,721 --> 00:25:58,789
THE CENTRE FERTILITY CLINIC?

366
00:25:58,858 --> 00:26:00,758
I HAVE NO FOND MEMORIES
OF THAT PLACE.

367
00:26:04,530 --> 00:26:06,463
HERE.

368
00:26:13,672 --> 00:26:19,076
"AA8585."
IS THAT A FILE NUMBER?

369
00:26:19,144 --> 00:26:23,980
- FROM NUGENESIS?
- DOES THAT HAVE ANYTHING TO DO
WITH THIS MAN ETHAN?

370
00:26:35,895 --> 00:26:40,530
FOLLOW NUGENESIS.
FOLLOW HIM.

371
00:26:43,836 --> 00:26:46,270
FOLLOW HIM.

372
00:26:48,207 --> 00:26:51,042
EMILY? EMILY?

373
00:26:58,618 --> 00:27:02,620
<i> YOU KNOW,</i>
<i> IF YOU CONSIDER YOURSELF</i>
<i> ANY KIND OF FRIEND OF HERS,</i>

374
00:27:02,688 --> 00:27:04,688
<i> YOU'LL DESTROY THOSE DISKS.</i>

375
00:27:04,756 --> 00:27:07,457
- AND YOU WILL DESTROY IT NOW!
- BUT I CAN'T!

376
00:27:07,527 --> 00:27:09,993
I CAN'T, SYDNEY.
I DON'T REALLY HAVE A CHOICE
IN THE MATTER, DO I?

377
00:27:10,062 --> 00:27:12,763
<i>I MEAN,</i>
<i>THIS IS MISS PARKER'S LIFE.</i>

378
00:27:12,832 --> 00:27:16,132
- THIS IS HER PAST.
SHE HAS EVERY RIGHT TO SEE IT.
- SEE WHAT?

379
00:27:19,271 --> 00:27:21,639
DO WHAT YOU MUST, BROOTS.

380
00:27:21,707 --> 00:27:26,843
BUT I WON'T BE A PART
OF OPENING THIS PANDORA'S BOX.

381
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:29,813
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>WHAT PANDORA'S BOX?</i>

382
00:27:29,882 --> 00:27:32,716
<i>[ Broots ]</i>
<i>I WAS ABLE TO RECONSTRUCT</i>
<i>ONE TINY PIECE OF THE DISKS...</i>

383
00:27:32,785 --> 00:27:35,152
<i>WE FOUND AT</i>
<i>RAINES'S FOREST HOUSE.</i>

384
00:27:35,221 --> 00:27:38,388
THE SAME PLACE WE WERE TODAY?
YEAH, BUT-- JUST WATCH.

385
00:27:42,428 --> 00:27:44,561
[ Raines ]
I HOPE YOU'RE FEELING
COMFORTABLE HERE, CATHERINE,

386
00:27:44,629 --> 00:27:47,498
AFTER ALL YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH.

387
00:27:47,566 --> 00:27:51,334
I NEVER THOUGHT I'D SEE THE DAY
WHEN I'D BE THANKING YOU
FOR YOUR KINDNESS, DR. RAINES.

388
00:27:51,403 --> 00:27:53,404
BUT THANK YOU.

389
00:27:53,472 --> 00:27:56,273
MY MOTHER WAS THERE.
<i> YEAH. BUT WHAT'S IMPORTANT</i>
<i> IS THE DATE.</i>

390
00:27:56,342 --> 00:27:59,877
<i> LOOK. LOOK AT THE DATE CODE</i>
<i> ON THE D.S.A.</i>

391
00:27:59,946 --> 00:28:03,747
<i>YOUR MOTHER WAS SHOT AND KILLED</i>
<i>AT THE CENTRE IN APRIL.</i>

392
00:28:03,816 --> 00:28:06,517
THIS SAYS JUNE.
THERE MUST BE A MIS--
<i> NO.</i>

393
00:28:06,586 --> 00:28:08,518
IT'S PHYSICALLY AND
TECHNICALLY IMPOSSIBLE...

394
00:28:08,588 --> 00:28:12,589
TO ALTER THE DATES
ON THE CENTRE D.S.A.
SURVEILLANCE SYSTEM.

395
00:28:12,658 --> 00:28:15,359
<i> SYDNEY DIDN'T WANT ME</i>
<i> TO SHOW YOU THIS.</i>
<i> I DON'T KNOW WHY.</i>

396
00:28:15,428 --> 00:28:17,360
BUT IT'S A LOCK.

397
00:28:17,430 --> 00:28:19,696
YOUR MOTHER DID NOT DIE
IN THAT ELEVATOR, MISS PARKER.

398
00:28:19,765 --> 00:28:24,234
ARE-- ARE YOU SAYING
MY MOTHER IS STILL ALIVE?

399
00:28:33,546 --> 00:28:37,047
<i>YOUR MOTHER ALIVE?</i>
<i>DOES THIS MAKE ANY SENSE?</i>

400
00:28:37,116 --> 00:28:41,184
<i>DO YOU THINK THAT WAS HERS?</i>
I DON'T REMEMBER IT,
BUT ANYTHING'S POSSIBLE.

401
00:28:41,253 --> 00:28:45,889
KEEP DECODING
THE FOREST HOUSE ARCHIVES.
AND DON'T TELL ANYONE.

402
00:28:45,958 --> 00:28:48,492
NOT EVEN SYDNEY?
ESPECIALLY SYDNEY.

403
00:28:48,561 --> 00:28:50,661
HE'S DONE EVERYTHING
EXCEPT HANDCUFF ME
TO A FREIGHT TRAIN...

404
00:28:50,729 --> 00:28:52,695
TO KEEP ME
FROM DIGGING INTO THIS.

405
00:28:52,764 --> 00:28:56,066
THERE MUST BE SOMEONE
YOU CAN TRUST.

406
00:28:56,135 --> 00:28:59,436
WHERE'S ANGELO?

407
00:29:04,676 --> 00:29:07,911
LOOKS LIKE THE SAME KIND
OF INSANITY I GREW UP WITH.

408
00:29:09,482 --> 00:29:12,416
<i>ARE YOU SURE</i>
<i>THIS IS THE ADDRESS</i>
<i>EMILY GAVE US FOR ETHAN?</i>

409
00:29:12,485 --> 00:29:15,418
POSITIVE.

410
00:29:15,487 --> 00:29:19,690
HE'S BEEN VIDEOTAPING
HIMSELF FOR YEARS.

411
00:29:19,758 --> 00:29:22,159
<i> IS THERE ANYTHING</i>
<i> ON NUGENESIS AA8585?</i>

412
00:29:22,228 --> 00:29:25,896
NOPE. BUT THERE'S ENOUGH
MATERIAL HERE TO WRITE
A DISSERTATION ON BOMB-MAKING.

413
00:29:25,964 --> 00:29:27,898
BUT THIS GUY'S
TAKEN IT A STEP FURTHER.

414
00:29:27,967 --> 00:29:29,800
HE'S DESIGNING HIS OWN BOMB.

415
00:29:37,943 --> 00:29:42,712
HUH. LOOK.
THERE'S AN UNMAILED LETTER...

416
00:29:42,781 --> 00:29:45,782
TO HIS PARENTS,
THE CLAUSENS.

417
00:29:45,851 --> 00:29:49,720
ACCORDING TO THIS TIME CODE,
THIS VIDEO WAS MADE
LESS THAN ONE HOUR AGO.

418
00:29:51,991 --> 00:29:54,591
THERE'S YOUR LITTLE BOMB-MAKER.
LET'S SEE WHAT HE'S BEEN UP TO.

419
00:30:05,003 --> 00:30:08,638
- WHO'S HE TALKING TO?
-<i> I KNOW I SHOULDN'T YELL.</i>

420
00:30:08,706 --> 00:30:11,107
I WON'T BE BAD ANYMORE.

421
00:30:11,176 --> 00:30:13,677
ACCORDING TO EMILY'S NOTES,

422
00:30:13,745 --> 00:30:16,279
THERE WERE SIGNS
OF ERRATIC BEHAVIOR,
OF MULTIPLE PERSONALITIES.

423
00:30:16,347 --> 00:30:18,481
HE MUST BE WRESTLING WITH
SOME KIND OF DEMONS INSIDE.

424
00:30:18,550 --> 00:30:21,451
EMILY SAID HE COULD HEAR
THE VOICES,
WHATEVER THAT MEANS.

425
00:30:21,520 --> 00:30:25,389
[ Phone Ringing ]

426
00:30:25,457 --> 00:30:29,526
YEAH?
HEY, HEY, LISTEN.

427
00:30:29,595 --> 00:30:31,628
I'M IN TROUBLE.
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

428
00:30:31,697 --> 00:30:35,565
<i> YES, I'M-I'M ALMOST READY</i>
<i> WITH 7677.</i>

429
00:30:35,634 --> 00:30:39,603
I-I JUST NEED A FEW MORE
COMPONENTS. BUT I'M TELLIN' YOU,
I NEED TO TALK.

430
00:30:39,671 --> 00:30:42,205
YOU SWEAR THAT
AFTER THE EXPLOSION,

431
00:30:42,273 --> 00:30:44,207
THE PAIN WILL BE GONE?

432
00:30:44,276 --> 00:30:48,111
<i>THEY'RE PROMISING HIM HIS INNER</i>
<i>TORTURE WILL END IF HE PULLS OFF</i>
<i>SOME KIND OF BOMBING FOR THEM.</i>

433
00:30:48,180 --> 00:30:50,980
- THE CENTRE.
- WHO ELSE?

434
00:30:51,049 --> 00:30:53,049
OKAY, I'LL DO IT. FIRST,
I WANNA SEE MY MOM AND DAD.

435
00:30:53,117 --> 00:30:57,220
<i> WHY WON'T YOU LET ME SEE</i>
<i> MY MOM AND DAD?</i>
<i> IT'S BEEN SO LONG.</i>

436
00:30:57,289 --> 00:30:59,322
I-I-I WROTE THEM A LETTER.

437
00:30:59,390 --> 00:31:01,824
<i> WHY CAN'T I SEND IT?</i>

438
00:31:01,893 --> 00:31:04,060
THEY DO LOVE ME!

439
00:31:07,299 --> 00:31:09,299
I KNOW.

440
00:31:11,103 --> 00:31:13,370
I KNOW YOU DO TOO.

441
00:31:14,806 --> 00:31:17,140
<i> [ Line Disconnects,</i>
<i> Dial Tone ]</i>

442
00:31:19,578 --> 00:31:21,912
[ Grunts ]

443
00:31:25,049 --> 00:31:29,019
- WHAT? ARE YOU SURE?
- WHAT'S HE DOING?

444
00:31:29,087 --> 00:31:33,756
- HE'S TALKING TO THE VOICES.
- HE'S GONNA-- HE'S GONNA HURT
MY MOM AND DAD?

445
00:31:33,825 --> 00:31:35,758
HE CAN'T HURT
MY MOM AND DAD.

446
00:31:37,496 --> 00:31:40,029
<i>[ Major Charles ]</i>
<i>WHEREVER HE'S GOING,</i>
<i>HE'S NOT COMING BACK,</i>

447
00:31:40,098 --> 00:31:42,032
<i>AND HE'S TAKING</i>
<i>HIS BOMB WITH HIM.</i>

448
00:31:48,173 --> 00:31:50,239
COME ON.
LET'S GO.

449
00:31:54,846 --> 00:31:58,781
<i>IT'S NOT MY FAULT</i>
<i>THAT JAROD FOUND HIS SISTER</i>
<i>BEFORE THE SWEEPER TEAM DID.</i>

450
00:31:58,850 --> 00:32:01,417
IT'S YOUR FAULT
SHE WAS STILL ALIVE.

451
00:32:01,486 --> 00:32:04,020
WELL, WHAT DID YOU TEACH ME
ABOUT WATER UNDER THE BRIDGE?

452
00:32:04,088 --> 00:32:06,522
IF IT GETS DEEP ENOUGH,
IT'LL DROWN YOU.
WHAT ABOUT MIRAGE?

453
00:32:06,591 --> 00:32:08,858
WE'RE STILL SEARCHING.
OH, THAT'S PERFECT.

454
00:32:08,927 --> 00:32:10,894
MY DAUGHTER IS SEARCHING
FOR A GHOST,

455
00:32:10,962 --> 00:32:13,963
MY SON IS SEARCHING
FOR A MONSTER.

456
00:32:14,032 --> 00:32:16,433
LAST ONE ALIVE WINS, HMM?

457
00:32:21,806 --> 00:32:24,273
<i>[ Angelo ]</i>
<i>SECRETS AND LIES.</i>

458
00:32:27,212 --> 00:32:29,379
SECRETS AND LIES.

459
00:32:29,448 --> 00:32:33,983
WHEN IT COMES TO THE CENTRE,
ANGELO, SECRETS AND LIES
ARE LIKE OXYGEN.

460
00:32:34,052 --> 00:32:35,985
LIES.

461
00:32:36,054 --> 00:32:40,423
ANGELO, I NEED YOU
TO EMPATH THIS FOR ME.

462
00:32:42,360 --> 00:32:45,128
IT MAY HAVE BELONGED
TO MY MOTHER.

463
00:32:47,499 --> 00:32:53,102
YOUR MOTHER WORE THIS.
HER JOURNEY NOT OVER.

464
00:32:55,474 --> 00:32:58,008
MY MOTHER IS STILL OUT THERE?

465
00:32:58,076 --> 00:33:01,010
ILLUSIONS ARE REAL.

466
00:33:01,079 --> 00:33:04,080
WHAT'S THAT MEAN?

467
00:33:06,852 --> 00:33:09,285
MIRAGES ARE REAL.

468
00:33:09,354 --> 00:33:11,855
WHAT'S "MIRAGE," ANGELO?

469
00:33:11,923 --> 00:33:15,792
MIRAGES ARE REAL.

470
00:33:17,262 --> 00:33:19,662
TELL ME WHAT THAT MEANS!

471
00:33:19,731 --> 00:33:24,667
MISS PARKER. HE--
HE'S ON YOUR SIDE.

472
00:33:24,736 --> 00:33:26,836
ANGELO SORRY.

473
00:33:26,904 --> 00:33:29,371
HE DOESN'T KNOW THE ANSWERS.

474
00:33:33,612 --> 00:33:35,612
BUT SYDNEY KNOWS.

475
00:33:37,049 --> 00:33:40,784
SYDNEY KNOWS ALL
THE SECRETS AND LIES.

476
00:34:01,272 --> 00:34:04,040
<i> [ Sobbing ]</i>
<i> OH, PLEASE.</i>

477
00:34:04,108 --> 00:34:06,542
<i> PLEASE DON'T BE DEAD.</i>
<i> PLEASE.</i>

478
00:34:12,884 --> 00:34:15,719
<i>[ Sobbing ]</i>
<i>DON'T LEAVE ME.</i>

479
00:34:17,589 --> 00:34:20,223
PLEASE DON'T LEAVE.
PLEASE.
<i>[ Voices Whispering ]</i>

480
00:34:25,130 --> 00:34:28,098
YOU DID THIS.

481
00:34:28,166 --> 00:34:30,099
NO, I SWEAR
I DIDN'T DO THIS.

482
00:34:30,168 --> 00:34:32,401
YOU HURT THEM!

483
00:34:37,776 --> 00:34:40,877
WHY? WHY?

484
00:34:40,946 --> 00:34:43,012
ETHAN, I DIDN'T HURT THEM.
I SWEAR TO YOU.

485
00:34:43,081 --> 00:34:45,047
<i>I DID NOT KILL THEM.</i>

486
00:34:46,484 --> 00:34:49,285
<i>[ Voices Whispering ]</i>
SOMEBODY HURT THEM.

487
00:34:49,354 --> 00:34:51,454
SOMEBODY KILLED MY PARENTS.

488
00:34:51,523 --> 00:34:53,890
<i> PLEASE, LET ME HELP YOU.</i>

489
00:34:56,694 --> 00:34:59,428
- HELP?
- MY SISTER EMILY,

490
00:34:59,497 --> 00:35:02,198
<i> SHE FOLLOWED YOU BECAUSE</i>
<i> SHE WANTED TO HELP YOU.</i>
<i>[ Sirens Wailing ]</i>

491
00:35:02,267 --> 00:35:05,468
- THAT'S ALL I WANT TO DO.
- THERE'S NO HELP FOR ME.

492
00:35:05,537 --> 00:35:08,971
<i>[ Tires Screeching ]</i>
<i>NOT FROM YOU. THERE'S ONLY</i>
<i>ONE PERSON WHO CAN HELP ME NOW.</i>

493
00:35:15,947 --> 00:35:17,914
ETHAN! ETHAN!

494
00:35:17,982 --> 00:35:21,217
FREEZE!
I'M F.B.I.
IT'S OKAY. IT'S OKAY.

495
00:35:21,286 --> 00:35:23,319
<i> F.B.I.</i>

496
00:35:23,388 --> 00:35:26,488
- THERE WERE REPORTS
OF SHOTS FIRED.
- UPSTAIRS. TWO BODIES.

497
00:35:26,557 --> 00:35:28,324
I WAS TOO LATE.

498
00:35:34,999 --> 00:35:39,369
YOU KNEW MY MOTHER WAS ALIVE,
BUT YOU DIDN'T TELL ME?

499
00:35:39,437 --> 00:35:42,305
YES.

500
00:35:44,041 --> 00:35:49,012
THEN GIVE ME ONE GOOD REASON
NOT TO BLOW
YOUR FLEMISH BRAINS OUT.

501
00:35:57,022 --> 00:35:59,522
I PROMISED HER
I WOULDN'T TELL YOU.

502
00:36:02,994 --> 00:36:06,462
[ Sighs ]
WELL, AS YOU KNOW,

503
00:36:06,531 --> 00:36:10,133
I GAVE YOUR MOTHER
HER LAST PSYCHIATRIC SESSION...

504
00:36:10,201 --> 00:36:12,935
<i> LESS THAN AN HOUR</i>
<i> BEFORE HER SUPPOSED MURDER.</i>

505
00:36:13,004 --> 00:36:17,540
SUPPOSED SUICIDE
IN THE ELEVATOR.
"SUPPOSED."

506
00:36:17,608 --> 00:36:20,577
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN, SYDNEY?

507
00:36:29,988 --> 00:36:33,423
<i> CATHERINE?</i>
<i> CATHERINE, PLEASE RELAX.</i>

508
00:36:33,491 --> 00:36:38,694
SYDNEY, I JUST FOUND OUT
THAT SOMEONE I LOVE
IS PLANNING TO KILL ME.

509
00:36:38,763 --> 00:36:42,732
-<i> WHO?</i>
- I CAN'T TELL YOU.
A FRIEND.

510
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:45,168
BUT IT'S FORCING ME TO--

511
00:36:45,236 --> 00:36:49,038
TO MAKE A VERY
DIFFICULT DECISION.

512
00:36:49,107 --> 00:36:52,675
I'M GOING TO STAGE MY DEATH
IN HOPES OF SAVING MY LIFE.

513
00:36:52,743 --> 00:36:55,511
<i> I DON'T UNDERSTAND.</i>
<i>AND I DON'T HAVE TIME</i>
<i>TO EXPLAIN IT ALL.</i>

514
00:36:55,580 --> 00:36:57,513
<i>BUT YOU KNOW THESE PEOPLE,</i>
<i>WHAT THEY'RE CAPABLE OF.</i>

515
00:36:57,582 --> 00:36:59,882
I TRY NOT TO IMAGINE.

516
00:36:59,951 --> 00:37:02,552
THEIR LATEST IS
A PROJECT CALLED MIRAGE,

517
00:37:02,620 --> 00:37:04,954
AND THEY'VE MADE ME
A KEY PLAYER.

518
00:37:05,022 --> 00:37:09,591
MY ONLY WAY OUT IS DYING,
BY THEIR HANDS OR MY OWN.

519
00:37:09,660 --> 00:37:12,662
<i> [ Sydney ]</i>
<i> THIS IS DANGEROUS TALK.</i>

520
00:37:12,731 --> 00:37:16,098
<i>THESE ARE DANGEROUS TIMES,</i>
<i>SYDNEY. I'LL DO</i>
<i>WHAT I HAVE TO TO SURVIVE.</i>

521
00:37:16,167 --> 00:37:19,935
AND THEN I'LL COME BACK
AND RESCUE JAROD AND ANGELO
AND MY LITTLE GIRL.

522
00:37:20,004 --> 00:37:22,238
WHAT ABOUT YOUR LITTLE GIRL?

523
00:37:24,475 --> 00:37:26,709
SHE'S MY GIFT FROM GOD,

524
00:37:26,778 --> 00:37:32,682
<i>AND I DON'T KNOW HOW TO SAVE HER</i>
<i>WITHOUT CAUSING HER THIS PAIN.</i>

525
00:37:32,751 --> 00:37:35,951
<i>PROMISE ME, SYDNEY.</i>
<i>SWEAR TO ME</i>
<i>THAT YOU'LL PROTECT HER,</i>

526
00:37:36,020 --> 00:37:37,953
THAT YOU'LL NEVER
TELL HER ABOUT THIS.

527
00:37:38,023 --> 00:37:39,955
YOU OWE ME.
I KNOW I DO.

528
00:37:40,025 --> 00:37:42,625
WHATEVER HAPPENS,
NO MATTER HOW BADLY
SHE WANTS TO KNOW,

529
00:37:42,694 --> 00:37:47,430
I DON'T WANT MY BABY GIRL
TO EVER HAVE
TO FACE THE TRUE TRAGEDY...

530
00:37:47,498 --> 00:37:50,700
OF HER FAMILY'S SECRET.

531
00:37:50,768 --> 00:37:54,036
- PROMISE ME.
-<i> I PROMISE.</i>

532
00:38:11,322 --> 00:38:13,255
GODSPEED, CATHERINE.

533
00:38:19,664 --> 00:38:23,166
<i> AN HOUR LATER,</i>
<i> THE GUNSHOT RANG OUT.</i>

534
00:38:23,234 --> 00:38:27,303
YOU KNOW THE REST.
I NEVER SAW CATHERINE AGAIN.

535
00:38:28,573 --> 00:38:31,808
- DO YOU KNOW WHAT IT IS?
- WHAT?

536
00:38:31,877 --> 00:38:37,247
MIRAGE. THE TRAGEDY...
OF MY FAMILY'S SECRET?

537
00:38:37,315 --> 00:38:42,652
I'M AFRAID I DON'T.
THAT IS THE TRUTH.

538
00:38:47,024 --> 00:38:51,961
<i>ETHAN'S PARENTS WERE MURDERED</i>
<i>AS A MESSAGE TO HIM.</i>

539
00:38:52,030 --> 00:38:56,765
<i>FINISH THE 7677 BOMBING,</i>
<i>OR ELSE. SOUNDS LIKE A MESSAGE</i>
<i>FROM THE CENTRE TO ME.</i>

540
00:38:56,834 --> 00:39:01,537
THAT HAS THE CENTRE
FINGERPRINTS ALL OVER IT.
THIS TOO.

541
00:39:01,605 --> 00:39:04,607
<i> YOU HACKED INTO</i>
<i> THE NUGENESIS MAINFRAME?</i>
UH-HUH.

542
00:39:04,675 --> 00:39:07,843
AND YOU WON'T BELIEVE
WHAT I FOUND
IN FILE NUMBER AA8585.

543
00:39:10,114 --> 00:39:12,548
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>AA8585 WAS A SHIPMENT...</i>

544
00:39:12,617 --> 00:39:15,284
<i>OF CRYOGENICALLY FROZEN</i>
<i>SPERM SAMPLES.</i>

545
00:39:15,353 --> 00:39:18,153
THEY WERE AIRLIFTED
TO THE CENTRE DECADES AGO.

546
00:39:18,222 --> 00:39:20,756
SOMEONE WANTED
TO GET PREGNANT PRETTY BADLY.

547
00:39:20,825 --> 00:39:23,859
YEAH, BUT THEY WEREN'T
JUST ANYONE'S SAMPLES, JAROD.

548
00:39:23,928 --> 00:39:25,995
THEY WERE MINE.

549
00:39:34,238 --> 00:39:36,639
HOW MUCH DOES JAROD KNOW?
[ Lyle ]
WE'RE NOT SURE.

550
00:39:36,708 --> 00:39:40,109
BUT MAJOR CHARLES'S
SEMINAL RECORDS HAVE BEEN
COMPROMISED AT NUGENESIS.

551
00:39:40,178 --> 00:39:42,979
[ Lyle ] AND THERE'S MORE.
JAROD WAS SPOTTED
AT THE PARENTS' HOUSE.

552
00:39:43,048 --> 00:39:46,515
- BEFORE OR AFTER
THEY WERE KILLED?
- AFTER, THANK GOD.

553
00:39:46,584 --> 00:39:50,052
- AND MIRAGE?
- [ Sighs ]

554
00:39:50,121 --> 00:39:51,687
HE'S STILL OUT THERE.

555
00:39:51,756 --> 00:39:55,324
THERE'S GOTTA BE SOME WAY
TO GET TO JAROD
BEFORE HE BEATS US TO HIM.

556
00:39:55,393 --> 00:39:58,628
THERE IS ONE.
WE GIVE HIM SOMETHING...

557
00:39:58,696 --> 00:40:01,230
MORE IMPORTANT TO GO AFTER.

558
00:40:01,299 --> 00:40:04,667
SOMETHING NAMED ZOE.

559
00:40:04,736 --> 00:40:07,069
<i> [ Mr. Parker ]</i>
<i> GOOD THINKING, MR. COX.</i>

560
00:40:07,138 --> 00:40:09,071
<i>[ Major Charles ]</i>
<i>IT ONLY GETS</i>
<i>STRANGER AND STRANGER.</i>

561
00:40:09,140 --> 00:40:11,841
MORE ON YOUR RECORDS
AT NUGENESIS?
YEAH.

562
00:40:11,909 --> 00:40:14,443
FOR THE PAST 25 YEARS,
COMPARATIVE GENETIC TEST
FOLLOW-UPS...

563
00:40:14,512 --> 00:40:16,879
HAVE BEEN CONDUCTED
USING MY D.N.A.

564
00:40:16,948 --> 00:40:19,882
THE QUESTION IS,
WHO OR WHAT
ARE THEY COMPARING IT TO?

565
00:40:19,951 --> 00:40:24,587
IT DOESN'T SAY.
BUT THE RESULTS WERE SENT
TO A PRIVATE RESIDENCE...

566
00:40:24,656 --> 00:40:26,588
IN BLUE COVE, DELAWARE.

567
00:40:29,493 --> 00:40:31,427
COME ON.

568
00:40:41,873 --> 00:40:44,273
[ Engine Starts ]

569
00:40:47,112 --> 00:40:49,045
OKAY, LET'S GO.

570
00:40:51,282 --> 00:40:53,782
YOU ALL RIGHT?

571
00:40:53,851 --> 00:40:57,052
SOMETHING FEELS...
WEIRD.

572
00:40:57,122 --> 00:41:01,056
WE'RE TALKIN' MR. RAINES.
IT'S SUPPOSED TO BE WEIRD.
NO.

573
00:41:01,126 --> 00:41:03,392
THIS IS WEIRDER THAN HIM.

574
00:41:15,806 --> 00:41:19,108
WHAT ARE WE LOOKIN' FOR?
THE TRUTH.

575
00:41:19,177 --> 00:41:21,411
I'LL CHECK OVER HERE.

576
00:41:21,479 --> 00:41:24,013
NO.

577
00:41:24,082 --> 00:41:26,282
IT'S NOT OVER THERE.

578
00:41:26,351 --> 00:41:28,418
HOW DO YOU KNOW, SON?

579
00:41:28,486 --> 00:41:30,753
I JUST KNOW. IT'S--

580
00:41:30,821 --> 00:41:33,456
IT'S LIKE
A STRANGE DÉJÀ VU.

581
00:41:35,292 --> 00:41:39,628
WHAT ARE YOU MUMBLING ABOUT?
I DECODED SOME OF THE ARCHIVES
FROM THE FOREST HOUSE.

582
00:41:39,697 --> 00:41:43,933
AND, WELL,
IF A PICTURE'S WORTH
MORE THAN A THOUSAND WORDS,

583
00:41:44,001 --> 00:41:46,335
I THINK I'VE JUST
UNCOVERED A THESAURUS.

584
00:41:46,403 --> 00:41:48,804
THIS IS ABOUT SIX MONTHS
AFTER YOUR MOTHER
SUPPOSEDLY DIED.

585
00:41:51,275 --> 00:41:54,309
WELL?
HE'LL BE HERE
IN A FEW MINUTES.

586
00:41:54,378 --> 00:41:57,880
YOU SURE YOU WANNA DO THIS?
[ Sighs ]

587
00:41:57,948 --> 00:42:00,282
I HAVE TO.

588
00:42:16,868 --> 00:42:20,702
- WHAT? WHAT DID SHE HAVE TO DO?
- WELL, WAIT.
JUST WATCH THAT DOOR.

589
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:24,974
<i> LIKE YOU'VE SEEN</i>
<i> THIS PLACE BEFORE?</i>

590
00:42:30,048 --> 00:42:32,114
IT'S LIKE I'VE BEEN HERE BEFORE.

591
00:42:36,520 --> 00:42:40,989
[ Gasps ]
OH, MY GOD.

592
00:42:41,058 --> 00:42:46,128
JAROD OUT OF THE CENTRE?
IMPOSSIBLE. HOW COULD THAT BE?

593
00:42:46,197 --> 00:42:48,030
SECRETS AND LIES.

594
00:42:48,098 --> 00:42:51,200
- HI, JAROD.
- HELLO, MRS. PARKER.

595
00:42:51,269 --> 00:42:53,502
THANK YOU FOR COMING.

596
00:42:55,106 --> 00:42:57,707
CLOSE THE DOOR.

597
00:43:07,418 --> 00:43:11,754
GYNECOLOGICAL INSTRUMENTS?
WHAT IS ALL THIS STUFF?

598
00:43:11,822 --> 00:43:14,157
TOOLS OF THE TRADE.

599
00:43:15,927 --> 00:43:20,996
<i> A BIRTHING TABLE?</i>
THE QUESTION IS, WHOSE?

600
00:43:21,065 --> 00:43:23,232
<i> COME HERE, JAROD.</i>

601
00:43:27,304 --> 00:43:29,772
THERE'S SOMETHING
I WANNA TELL YOU.

602
00:43:31,942 --> 00:43:34,076
MY MOTHER WAS PREGNANT?

603
00:43:36,648 --> 00:43:39,214
YOU'RE GOING
TO HAVE A BROTHER.

604
00:43:40,618 --> 00:43:42,551
<i>[ Major Charles ]</i>
<i>THIS IS JUST TOO WEIRD.</i>

605
00:43:42,620 --> 00:43:44,686
BIRTHING TABLES,
INCUBATORS,

606
00:43:44,755 --> 00:43:46,955
GENETIC FOLLOW-UPS
OF MY SEMEN.

607
00:43:47,024 --> 00:43:50,559
ARE YOU THINKING
WHAT I'M THINKING?

608
00:43:50,628 --> 00:43:52,594
I HAVE A BROTHER.

609
00:43:52,663 --> 00:43:55,864
I HAVE A BROTHER?

610
00:43:55,933 --> 00:43:58,033
JAROD AND I
SHARE A BROTHER?

611
00:43:58,102 --> 00:44:01,303
IT MUST BE ETHAN.

612
00:44:02,973 --> 00:44:06,742
BUT WHERE IS HE?
<i>[ Ethan ]</i>
<i>MY PARENTS ARE GONE.</i>

613
00:44:06,811 --> 00:44:11,347
MOM IS DEAD.
DAD IS DEAD.

614
00:44:11,416 --> 00:44:13,415
[ Raines ]
I'M YOUR FATHER NOW.

615
00:44:26,163 --> 00:44:28,130
<i> [ Sydney ]</i>
<i> DETAILS ARE SKETCHY, JAROD.</i>

616
00:44:28,199 --> 00:44:31,767
I'M JUST NOW TRYING
TO PIECE A LOT OF THIS
TOGETHER MYSELF.

617
00:44:31,836 --> 00:44:37,106
THIS FEELING IS SO STRONG,
SYDNEY, THAT I'VE BEEN
TO THAT FOREST HOUSE BEFORE.

618
00:44:37,175 --> 00:44:39,842
BUT MY MIND
WANTS TO BLOCK IT OUT.

619
00:44:39,911 --> 00:44:42,744
<i>I HAVE A FEELING TOO, JAROD,</i>
<i>AND IT SAYS YOU'RE LYING.</i>

620
00:44:42,813 --> 00:44:47,082
MISS PARKER.
I'M GLAD TO HEAR YOUR MIND
HASN'T BLOCKED ME OUT YET.

621
00:44:47,151 --> 00:44:49,151
TELL HIM, SYD.
LIKE HE DOESN'T KNOW.

622
00:44:49,220 --> 00:44:52,921
<i>WELL, WE SAW THE D.S.A.,</i>
<i>AND YOU WERE DEFINITELY THERE.</i>

623
00:44:52,990 --> 00:44:55,991
THEN WHY DON'T I REMEMBER IT?
[ Miss Parker ]
YOU'RE THE GENIUS.

624
00:44:56,059 --> 00:44:59,695
- YOU TELL US.
-<i> IF I COULD I WOULD,</i>
<i>  MISS PARKER. YOU KNOW THAT.</i>

625
00:44:59,764 --> 00:45:01,864
I'VE NEVER HELD BACK
WHEN IT COMES TO YOUR MOTHER.

626
00:45:01,932 --> 00:45:04,700
[ Miss Parker ]
YOU WERE ON THE D.S.A., JAROD.
SHE TALKED TO YOU.

627
00:45:04,769 --> 00:45:06,935
SHE TOLD YOU SECRETS.
I DON'T REMEMBER.

628
00:45:10,274 --> 00:45:12,841
OR HOW IN THE HELL
THAT BABY SHE WAS CARRYING
IS YOUR BROTHER?

629
00:45:12,910 --> 00:45:17,012
- LOOK, I DON'T KNOW.
- OR WHERE SHE WAS GOING,
OR WHERE THE BABY WENT, OR--

630
00:45:17,081 --> 00:45:19,548
I DON'T KNOW!

631
00:45:19,617 --> 00:45:23,285
[ Sydney ]
IT IS ENTIRELY POSSIBLE THAT...

632
00:45:23,354 --> 00:45:26,955
YOUR SUBCONSCIOUS MIND
HAS BLOCKED OUT
THOSE RECOLLECTIONS, JAROD,

633
00:45:27,024 --> 00:45:29,858
EITHER BY ITSELF OR WITH
THE HELP OF SOMEONE ELSE.

634
00:45:29,927 --> 00:45:32,027
SO THOSE MEMORIES COULD
STILL BE IN JAROD'S HEAD?

635
00:45:32,096 --> 00:45:36,765
<i>EVERY WAKING MOMENT OF OUR LIVES</i>
<i>IS STORED SOMEWHERE</i>
<i>IN OUR MINDS.</i>

636
00:45:36,834 --> 00:45:38,967
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>WELL, FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH,</i>
<i>MISS PARKER, I BELIEVE THAT--</i>

637
00:45:40,971 --> 00:45:43,972
THAT OUR BROTHER
IS A MAN NAMED ETHAN.

638
00:45:44,041 --> 00:45:46,308
<i>NOW, I DON'T KNOW WHERE HE IS,</i>

639
00:45:46,377 --> 00:45:50,079
BUT SOMEHOW HE'S INVOLVED
WITH A PROJECT CALLED 7677.

640
00:45:50,148 --> 00:45:53,582
<i> YOU FIGURE OUT 7677,</i>

641
00:45:53,651 --> 00:45:55,784
YOU FIND BABY BROTHER.

642
00:46:00,291 --> 00:46:02,792
<i>[ Ethan ]</i>
<i>I'M ALMOST READY WITH 7677.</i>

643
00:46:02,860 --> 00:46:04,826
<i>I JUST NEED</i>
<i>A FEW MORE COMPONENTS.</i>

644
00:46:04,896 --> 00:46:07,630
BUT I'M TELLING YOU,
I NEED TO TALK. OKAY.

645
00:46:11,069 --> 00:46:13,069
[ Grunts ]

646
00:46:19,510 --> 00:46:21,444
STILL NOTHIN'
ON THIS GUY, AGENT?

647
00:46:21,512 --> 00:46:24,012
STILL NOTHING.
<i> [ Man ] YOU CAN'T DRAG ME</i>
<i> OUT OF MY HOUSE LIKE THAT!</i>

648
00:46:24,081 --> 00:46:26,449
I GOT A WHOLE GRILLED CHEESE
GOIN' RIGHT THERE
ON THE STOVE.

649
00:46:26,517 --> 00:46:29,618
HEY, WHERE DO YOU
WANT HIM, DETECTIVE?

650
00:46:29,687 --> 00:46:32,421
COME ON!
<i>[ Brookins ]</i>
<i>ASK, AND YE SHALL RECEIVE.</i>

651
00:46:32,490 --> 00:46:34,824
THAT'S THE LOCAL MUNITIONS GUY
YOU ASKED US TO HAUL IN.

652
00:46:34,892 --> 00:46:38,694
NAME'S JED SIDEL.
SMALL-TIME MIDDLE MAN,
ALL-AROUND WEASEL.

653
00:46:38,763 --> 00:46:42,798
WELL, WHAT A COINCIDENCE.
WEASEL SEASON HAS JUST OPENED.

654
00:46:45,603 --> 00:46:47,536
JED.

655
00:46:47,605 --> 00:46:50,439
<i>AGENT CURTIS, F.B.I.</i>
HELLO.

656
00:46:50,507 --> 00:46:52,842
ON BEHALF OF THE BUREAU,
I WOULD LIKE
TO SAY CONGRATULATIONS.

657
00:46:52,910 --> 00:46:54,710
HMM?
WELL, YOU'RE MOVING UP
IN THE WORLD.

658
00:46:54,779 --> 00:46:58,147
I AM?
AIDING AND ABETTING
IN THE MAKING OF BOMBS.

659
00:46:58,216 --> 00:47:02,384
HELPING TO MURDER INNOCENT
CITIZENS. I MEAN, THIS IS
HARDLY FENCING STOLEN TVs.

660
00:47:02,453 --> 00:47:05,720
YOU'RE HITTIN' THE BIG LEAGUES.
YOUR PARENTS MUST BE
VERY PROUD OF YOU.

661
00:47:05,789 --> 00:47:07,723
YOU GOT THE WRONG GUY.
REALLY?

662
00:47:07,792 --> 00:47:11,661
WELL, HE DOESN'T SEEM
TO THINK SO.

663
00:47:12,730 --> 00:47:14,796
I DON'T KNOW WHO THAT IS.

664
00:47:17,234 --> 00:47:19,635
THAT WASN'T MY QUESTION.
WHAT-WHAT-WHAT WAS
THE QUESTION?

665
00:47:19,704 --> 00:47:22,237
WHY ARE YOU HELPING
YOUR FRIEND HERE MAKE BOMBS?

666
00:47:25,276 --> 00:47:28,411
NO, NO. ETHAN
AIN'T NO FRIEND OF MINE.
ETHAN?

667
00:47:28,479 --> 00:47:31,614
I THOUGHT YOU DIDN'T KNOW HIM.

668
00:47:31,683 --> 00:47:34,082
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA WHAT
THIS GUY'S GONNA DO TO ME
IF I SPILL TO YOU?

669
00:47:34,151 --> 00:47:39,254
I MEAN, HE TALKS TO PEOPLE
THAT AREN'T EVEN THERE.
HE'S CRAZY.

670
00:47:39,323 --> 00:47:41,357
UNLIKE THE LOVABLE LIFERS
IN FEDERAL PRISON.

671
00:47:41,425 --> 00:47:45,194
HMM?
I HEAR SHOWER TIME'S
A REAL SCREAM, JED.

672
00:47:45,262 --> 00:47:49,431
EXPLOSIVES. YES.
HE WAS LOOKING FOR EXPLOSIVES.

673
00:47:49,500 --> 00:47:51,534
LIKE C-4, SEMTEX,
UH, DIGITAL FUSES.

674
00:47:51,602 --> 00:47:53,702
<i> AND ALL I DID,</i>
<i> AND THIS IS ALL I DID,</i>

675
00:47:53,771 --> 00:47:56,338
WAS CALL A GUY
ON THE PHONE, AND I--
AND I SET UP A MEETING.

676
00:47:56,407 --> 00:47:58,006
<i> THAT'S IT.</i>
WHERE AND WHEN?

677
00:47:58,075 --> 00:48:00,342
MM-HMM.

678
00:48:00,410 --> 00:48:04,246
AT THE WAREHOUSE AT MIDNIGHT.
BROAD STREET AND FRANKLIN.

679
00:48:16,227 --> 00:48:18,294
[ Engine Starts ]

680
00:48:30,708 --> 00:48:33,209
<i>THERE WAS ONLY ABOUT</i>
<i>ONE MINUTE OF STUFF</i>
<i>LEFT ON THE D.S.A.</i>

681
00:48:33,277 --> 00:48:35,611
BUT WHAT'S THERE
IS REALLY TELLING.

682
00:48:43,821 --> 00:48:47,289
DR. RAINES,
LEAVE US ALONE, PLEASE?

683
00:48:47,358 --> 00:48:51,460
CATHERINE, I DON'T THINK
THAT WOULD BE A GOOD IDEA.

684
00:48:51,529 --> 00:48:54,930
I THINK IT WOULD BE
A GREAT IDEA.

685
00:49:03,006 --> 00:49:06,308
<i> JAROD, THERE'S SOMETHING</i>
<i> I HAVE TO TELL YOU...</i>

686
00:49:06,377 --> 00:49:08,778
THAT YOU CAN NEVER FORGET.

687
00:49:08,846 --> 00:49:11,480
OKAY.

688
00:49:11,549 --> 00:49:14,183
I MAY NOT LIVE MUCH LONGER,
AND IF I DON'T,

689
00:49:14,251 --> 00:49:17,786
THERE'S SOMETHING VERY IMPORTANT
I WANT YOU TO TELL MY DAUGHTER.

690
00:49:17,855 --> 00:49:20,789
<i>WILL YOU PROMISE ME</i>
<i>THAT YOU'LL TELL HER?</i>

691
00:49:20,858 --> 00:49:22,958
I PROMISE.

692
00:49:23,026 --> 00:49:27,363
IT'S SOMETHING I DON'T EVER
WANT ANYONE ELSE TO HEAR.

693
00:49:32,670 --> 00:49:35,704
WHAT'S WRONG, BROOTS?
FIX IT.

694
00:49:35,773 --> 00:49:38,941
WELL, THERE'S NOTHING TO FIX.
SHE UNPLUGGED IT.
THAT'S ALL THERE IS.

695
00:49:39,009 --> 00:49:42,577
MY BUTT THAT'S ALL THERE IS.
MAKE IT TALK.

696
00:49:42,647 --> 00:49:46,615
I-I CAN'T.
MY MOTHER'S DYING SECRET.

697
00:49:46,684 --> 00:49:50,719
THE ONE THING
SHE WANTED ME TO KNOW...

698
00:49:50,788 --> 00:49:54,490
IS NOT ONLY LOST ELECTRONICALLY,
BUT SOMEWHERE INSIDE
JAROD'S HEAD,

699
00:49:54,559 --> 00:49:56,492
AND HE CAN'T REMEMBER
A THING.

700
00:49:56,561 --> 00:49:59,061
HMM.

701
00:49:59,129 --> 00:50:04,433
RAINES. RAINES MUST HAVE
ERASED THAT PORTION
OF JAROD'S BRAIN.

702
00:50:04,502 --> 00:50:08,136
YOU MEAN, LIKE, HYPNOTIZED HIM
OR BRAINWASHED HIM OR SOMETHING?
VERY LIKELY.

703
00:50:08,206 --> 00:50:11,139
<i> I DON'T KNOW HOW RAINES</i>
<i> LOCKED THAT MEMORY</i>
<i> IN GENIUS BOY'S MIND,</i>

704
00:50:11,208 --> 00:50:14,643
BUT I'M GONNA FREE IT UP
IF I HAVE TO CRACK
HIS HEAD OPEN...

705
00:50:14,712 --> 00:50:16,978
AND CARVE IT OUT
WITH A MELON SCOOPER.

706
00:50:17,047 --> 00:50:19,214
HOW ARE WE GONNA DO THAT?
<i>WE TRACK RAINES.</i>

707
00:50:19,283 --> 00:50:21,616
I'LL BET MY ASS
HE KNOWS WHERE ETHAN IS.

708
00:50:21,685 --> 00:50:24,853
WE FIND ETHAN,
WE FIND JAROD.

709
00:51:23,147 --> 00:51:25,147
MOVE IN, SAM!

710
00:51:32,290 --> 00:51:35,724
[ Chattering ]

711
00:51:59,650 --> 00:52:03,084
RELAX, SON. EVERYTHING'S
GOING TO BE JUST FINE.

712
00:52:03,153 --> 00:52:05,754
I FEEL SO ALONE.

713
00:52:05,823 --> 00:52:10,592
BUT YOU'RE NOT, ETHAN.
I'M HERE FOR YOU.
YOU KNOW THAT, DON'T YOU?

714
00:52:14,031 --> 00:52:17,966
<i>AFTER YOU EARN THE TRUST</i>
<i>OF THE TRIUMVIRATE</i>
<i>WITH THE BOMBING,</i>

715
00:52:18,035 --> 00:52:21,503
YOU'LL COME TO LIVE
AT THE CENTRE WHERE
WE'LL DO GREAT THINGS TOGETHER.

716
00:52:21,572 --> 00:52:24,539
<i>I'LL BE CALLING YOU SOON.</i>

717
00:52:30,280 --> 00:52:34,016
<i>[ Door Opens, Closes ]</i>

718
00:52:34,085 --> 00:52:36,952
<i> ETHAN? IT'S OKAY.</i>
<i> I'M NOT HERE TO HURT YOU.</i>

719
00:52:37,020 --> 00:52:39,154
NO, YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO KILLED MY PARENTS.

720
00:52:39,223 --> 00:52:41,323
I DIDN'T KILL YOUR PARENTS.

721
00:52:41,392 --> 00:52:43,525
<i>[ Voices Whispering ]</i>

722
00:52:43,594 --> 00:52:48,196
<i> HOW DO YOU KNOW</i>
<i> I CAN TRUST HIM?</i>
<i> I CAN'T TRUST ANYONE.</i>

723
00:52:48,265 --> 00:52:51,900
<i> NOT YOU, NOT HIM.</i>

724
00:52:51,969 --> 00:52:55,537
ETHAN, I'M YOUR FRIEND.

725
00:52:59,876 --> 00:53:03,378
- [ Chain Rattling ]
- ETHAN, RUN! RUN!

726
00:53:04,080 --> 00:53:06,582
[ Gunshot ]

727
00:53:10,721 --> 00:53:12,654
<i> [ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i> JAROD!</i>

728
00:53:15,392 --> 00:53:18,193
DAMN IT!

729
00:53:31,742 --> 00:53:36,010
<i> JAROD! YOUR NINTH LIFE</i>
<i> JUST RAN OUT.</i>

730
00:53:41,218 --> 00:53:43,319
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>YOU LOOK SURPRISED TO BE HERE.</i>

731
00:53:43,387 --> 00:53:47,989
WELL, I'M SURPRISED
I'M STILL ALIVE.

732
00:53:48,058 --> 00:53:50,525
DEAD MEN TELL NO TALES.

733
00:53:50,594 --> 00:53:55,263
I'M ASSUMING SINCE WE'RE HERE,
THIS HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH CENTRE BUSINESS?

734
00:53:55,332 --> 00:53:58,167
NO.

735
00:54:04,008 --> 00:54:07,776
IT'S ABOUT ME.
I NEED YOUR HELP.

736
00:54:09,779 --> 00:54:13,983
TELL ME WHAT I NEED TO KNOW,
AND YOU'RE OUT OF HERE.

737
00:54:14,051 --> 00:54:18,320
AND I SHOULD BELIEVE
YOU'RE GOING TO LET ME
JUST WALK AWAY? HMM?

738
00:54:29,233 --> 00:54:31,233
WATCH THIS, JAROD.

739
00:54:33,170 --> 00:54:35,303
[ Young Jarod ]
HELLO, MRS. PARKER.
THANK YOU FOR COMING.

740
00:54:35,372 --> 00:54:37,706
CLOSE THE DOOR.

741
00:54:40,144 --> 00:54:42,410
<i>COME HERE, JAROD.</i>

742
00:54:44,949 --> 00:54:47,149
<i>THERE'S SOMETHING</i>
<i>I WANNA TELL YOU.</i>

743
00:54:51,388 --> 00:54:53,755
YOU'RE GOING
TO HAVE A BROTHER.

744
00:55:00,297 --> 00:55:03,932
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>I DON'T REMEMBER THIS.</i>
<i>SYDNEY, I DON'T REMEMBER THIS.</i>

745
00:55:04,001 --> 00:55:07,502
<i>[ Sydney ]</i>
<i>IT'S IN YOUR MIND SOMEWHERE.</i>

746
00:55:07,571 --> 00:55:10,505
THEN LET'S GET IT OUT.

747
00:55:13,410 --> 00:55:18,113
<i>THREE, TWO, ONE.</i>

748
00:55:22,886 --> 00:55:24,886
GO BACK INTO YOUR MEMORY, JAROD,

749
00:55:24,955 --> 00:55:28,122
<i>TO WHEN YOU WERE A YOUNG BOY.</i>

750
00:55:28,191 --> 00:55:30,191
<i>ARE YOU THERE NOW?</i>

751
00:55:31,762 --> 00:55:37,299
<i>GO BACK TO A MOMENT</i>
<i>WHEN RAINES CAME</i>
<i>TO TAKE YOU FROM THE CENTRE.</i>

752
00:55:37,368 --> 00:55:40,402
<i>AND WHERE DID HE TAKE YOU?</i>

753
00:55:40,471 --> 00:55:43,372
<i> [ Jarod ]</i>
<i> A HOUSE IN THE WOODS.</i>

754
00:55:43,440 --> 00:55:47,542
<i>CAN YOU SEE THE HOUSE NOW?</i>
<i> YES.</i>

755
00:55:47,611 --> 00:55:50,479
<i>GO INSIDE.</i>

756
00:55:50,547 --> 00:55:54,016
<i>ARE YOU THERE?</i>
<i> YES.</i>

757
00:55:54,084 --> 00:55:59,021
<i> I SMELL WOOD.</i>
<i> WOOD PANELING. CEDAR.</i>

758
00:55:59,089 --> 00:56:01,656
<i>VERY GOOD, JAROD.</i>

759
00:56:01,725 --> 00:56:06,094
<i> I WALK THROUGH</i>
<i> A SLIDING DOOR.</i>

760
00:56:06,163 --> 00:56:08,229
<i> SHE'S THERE.</i>
<i>WHO IS?</i>

761
00:56:08,298 --> 00:56:11,199
<i> CATHERINE PARKER.</i>
<i> SHE'S STILL ALIVE.</i>

762
00:56:11,268 --> 00:56:13,268
HI, JAROD.

763
00:56:15,305 --> 00:56:17,305
SHE DIDN'T DIE
IN THE ELEVATOR.

764
00:56:19,910 --> 00:56:23,611
<i> SHE SEEMS TROUBLED.</i>
<i>BY WHAT?</i>

765
00:56:25,415 --> 00:56:27,749
SHE WANTS ME...

766
00:56:27,818 --> 00:56:30,852
TO TELL HER DAUGHTER
SOMETHING VERY IMPORTANT.

767
00:56:30,921 --> 00:56:32,788
WHAT?

768
00:56:34,291 --> 00:56:37,359
<i>IT'S VERY IMPORTANT THAT</i>
<i>SHE KNOW THE TRUTH ABOUT ETHAN.</i>

769
00:56:37,428 --> 00:56:39,427
ETHAN?

770
00:56:40,764 --> 00:56:43,331
THAT'S WHAT HE TOLD ME
HIS NAME WOULD BE.

771
00:56:43,400 --> 00:56:46,501
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
HOW WOULD HE KNOW?

772
00:56:46,570 --> 00:56:50,272
- HOW DO YOU?
- I CALL IT MY INNER SENSE.

773
00:56:50,340 --> 00:56:52,640
INNER SENSE?

774
00:56:52,710 --> 00:56:56,411
FOR MOST, IT'S THE HAIRS
ON THE BACK OF YOUR NECK,

775
00:56:56,480 --> 00:56:58,947
<i> OR THAT NERVOUS FEELING</i>
<i> IN YOUR STOMACH.</i>

776
00:56:59,015 --> 00:57:03,084
<i>[ Jarod, Mrs. Parker Together ]</i>
<i>FOR ME, IT'S VOICES</i>
<i>I HEAR ALL AROUND ME,</i>

777
00:57:03,153 --> 00:57:05,620
USUALLY WARNING ME OF THINGS
THAT ARE ABOUT TO HAPPEN.

778
00:57:05,689 --> 00:57:07,655
LIKE SOULS TALKING TO YOU?

779
00:57:07,724 --> 00:57:09,891
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

780
00:57:09,960 --> 00:57:13,728
<i> I'VE BEEN BLESSED</i>
<i> WITH THIS GIFT, JAROD.</i>

781
00:57:13,797 --> 00:57:16,464
AND THOUGH SHE DOESN'T KNOW IT,
SO HAS MY DAUGHTER.

782
00:57:16,533 --> 00:57:19,568
<i>THOUGH NEITHER OF US</i>
<i>QUITE LIKE ETHAN.</i>

783
00:57:19,637 --> 00:57:24,406
<i>I JUST PRAY HIS GIFT ISN'T</i>
<i>ABUSED BY THE WRONG PEOPLE.</i>

784
00:57:24,475 --> 00:57:26,408
<i>[ Young Jarod ]</i>
<i>WHY ARE YOU TELLING ME THIS?</i>

785
00:57:26,476 --> 00:57:29,578
BECAUSE ETHAN
IS ALSO YOUR BROTHER.

786
00:57:29,647 --> 00:57:33,448
<i> UNKNOWN TO ME,</i>
<i> WHILE I WAS SEDATED...</i>

787
00:57:33,517 --> 00:57:36,751
FOR A MINOR SURGERY
NOT LONG AGO,

788
00:57:36,820 --> 00:57:40,555
MY HUSBAND...

789
00:57:40,624 --> 00:57:44,526
USED YOUR FATHER'S SEED
TO IMPREGNATE ME.

790
00:57:44,595 --> 00:57:47,528
- MY FATHER'S GENETICS.
- YES.

791
00:57:47,597 --> 00:57:49,864
<i> MR. PARKER WANTED</i>
<i> TO CREATE A CHILD...</i>

792
00:57:49,933 --> 00:57:52,334
WITH THIS INNER SENSE...

793
00:57:52,403 --> 00:57:54,669
WHO COULD ALSO
BE SPECIAL LIKE YOU ARE,

794
00:57:54,738 --> 00:57:58,339
<i> TO USE, NO DOUBT,</i>
<i> AS THEY HAVE USED YOU.</i>

795
00:58:01,044 --> 00:58:05,413
MR. RAINES SHOWED ME PROOF
OF WHAT HAD BEEN DONE...

796
00:58:05,482 --> 00:58:09,183
AND THAT MR. PARKER
IS PLANNING TO KILL ME...

797
00:58:09,252 --> 00:58:11,552
WHEN THE BABY IS BORN.

798
00:58:11,621 --> 00:58:14,989
<i>[ Young Jarod ]</i>
<i>MR. RAINES SCARES ME.</i>
<i>WHY DO YOU TRUST HIM?</i>

799
00:58:15,059 --> 00:58:18,893
I TRUSTED HIM BECAUSE--

800
00:58:18,962 --> 00:58:20,895
BECAUSE HE TRUSTED ME.

801
00:58:22,933 --> 00:58:25,199
THAT AND...

802
00:58:25,268 --> 00:58:30,071
IT WAS THE ONLY WAY FOR ME
TO GIVE THIS CHILD
A CHANCE AT A REAL LIFE.

803
00:58:31,642 --> 00:58:34,876
BUT NOW--

804
00:58:34,945 --> 00:58:37,245
SOMETHING'S WRONG.

805
00:58:37,313 --> 00:58:42,383
THE VOICES ARE TELLING ME
I WON'T LEAVE THIS HOUSE ALIVE.

806
00:58:43,921 --> 00:58:46,054
<i>[ Young Jarod ]</i>
<i>THAT'S WHY YOU BROUGHT ME HERE.</i>

807
00:58:48,659 --> 00:58:52,427
YOU'RE SPECIAL, JAROD,
AND I KNOW YOU WON'T FORGET.

808
00:58:53,763 --> 00:58:59,134
I WANT YOU TO TELL MY DAUGHTER
TO COMPLETE MY PLAN.

809
00:58:59,203 --> 00:59:02,436
<i>[ Young Jarod ]</i>
<i>PLAN?</i>

810
00:59:02,505 --> 00:59:07,509
<i> SHE'LL UNDERSTAND ONE DAY.</i>
<i> JUST TELL HER TO TRUST</i>
<i> HER INNER SENSE.</i>

811
00:59:07,577 --> 00:59:10,345
<i> IT WILL GUIDE HER ACTIONS.</i>

812
00:59:14,851 --> 00:59:20,088
<i> JAROD, YOUR SOUL</i>
<i> IS A TRUSTING ONE,</i>
<i> JUST LIKE YOUR MOTHER'S.</i>

813
00:59:20,156 --> 00:59:23,091
- YOU KNOW MY MOTHER?
- YES.

814
00:59:24,561 --> 00:59:28,363
AND ONE DAY,
YOU'LL BE BACK TOGETHER AGAIN.

815
00:59:28,432 --> 00:59:30,765
AND ETHAN WILL HELP YOU
FIND HER.

816
00:59:32,569 --> 00:59:38,473
<i>[ Jarod, Mrs. Parker Together ]</i>
<i>TRUST YOUR INNER SENSE.</i>

817
00:59:46,917 --> 00:59:49,718
<i>[ Typing ]</i>

818
01:00:38,902 --> 01:00:41,502
- MR. LYLE.
- ANY NEWS FROM COX ABOUT ZOE?

819
01:00:41,571 --> 01:00:43,504
<i>ACCORDING TO HIS LAST MESSAGE,</i>
<i>HE'S READY.</i>

820
01:00:43,573 --> 01:00:47,943
BUT THIS IS WHY I'M HERE.
OUR PEOPLE AT
TRIUMVIRATE HEADQUARTERS...

821
01:00:48,011 --> 01:00:50,479
THOUGHT YOU MIGHT FIND THAT
QUITE INTERESTING.

822
01:00:53,917 --> 01:00:56,785
RAINES HAS BEEN A BUSY BOY.

823
01:00:56,854 --> 01:00:59,454
<i>[ Broots ] I INTERCEPTED</i>
<i>A COMMUNIQUÉ BETWEEN</i>
<i>RAINES AND THE TRIUMVIRATE,</i>

824
01:00:59,522 --> 01:01:01,623
<i> AND I'M PROBABLY</i>
<i> NOT THE ONLY ONE WHO DID.</i>

825
01:01:01,691 --> 01:01:04,892
- SPIT IT OUT, BROOTS.
- IT'S ABOUT 7677.

826
01:01:04,961 --> 01:01:07,094
AND THAT THING,
THAT MIRAGE--

827
01:01:07,163 --> 01:01:09,364
THAT "THING" IS MY BROTHER.

828
01:01:09,433 --> 01:01:11,365
WHOA.

829
01:01:11,434 --> 01:01:15,036
<i> OKAY. IN A NUTSHELL,</i>
<i> THERE'S SOME PROJECT</i>
<i> CALLED 7677.</i>

830
01:01:15,104 --> 01:01:18,773
<i>AND IF IT GOES OFF AS PLANNED,</i>
<i>MR. RAINES IS GONNA</i>
<i>BE IN CHARGE OF THE CENTRE.</i>

831
01:01:18,842 --> 01:01:23,311
A RAINES COUP.
THANK YOU.

832
01:01:23,380 --> 01:01:25,380
HELLO?

833
01:01:27,884 --> 01:01:30,618
WHY DO I FEEL LIKE YOU KNOW
WHAT BROOTS JUST TOLD ME?

834
01:01:30,687 --> 01:01:36,491
RAINES HAS BEEN WORKING TOWARDS
THIS HIS WHOLE SORDID CAREER.
USING ETHAN.

835
01:01:36,560 --> 01:01:40,862
<i> HE TOOK HIM AS A CHILD,</i>
<i> PLACED HIM IN</i>
<i> A SURROGATE FAMILY...</i>

836
01:01:40,931 --> 01:01:44,299
WITH PEOPLE WHO WOULD ALLOW
RAINES TO CONTROL HIS EMOTIONS.

837
01:01:44,367 --> 01:01:47,602
<i> IN OTHER WORDS,</i>
<i> SCREWED HIM UP SO BADLY,</i>
<i> HE WOULD ONLY TRUST RAINES.</i>

838
01:01:47,671 --> 01:01:52,040
SO RAINES COULD HAVE
TOTAL CONTROL OVER HIM,

839
01:01:52,108 --> 01:01:54,242
TURN ETHAN INTO
HIS PRIVATE ASSASSIN.

840
01:01:54,311 --> 01:01:58,613
<i> AND WHEN RAINES KILLED</i>
<i> HIS SURROGATE PARENTS,</i>

841
01:01:58,682 --> 01:02:03,918
HE SEVERED ALL EMOTIONAL TIES
TO ANYTHING CONNECTED
WITH THE OUTSIDE WORLD.

842
01:02:03,986 --> 01:02:06,254
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>WELL, THAT IS</i>
<i>WHAT RAINES DOES BEST--</i>

843
01:02:06,323 --> 01:02:08,190
TAKE PEOPLE AWAY
FROM THEIR FAMILIES.

844
01:02:09,826 --> 01:02:11,626
WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO DO?

845
01:02:11,695 --> 01:02:13,695
[ Sighs ]

846
01:02:16,099 --> 01:02:18,366
I DON'T KNOW.

847
01:02:19,569 --> 01:02:22,370
<i>DO WHAT YOUR MOTHER</i>
<i>WOULD HAVE WANTED.</i>

848
01:02:22,439 --> 01:02:24,639
FINISH HER WORK.

849
01:02:26,343 --> 01:02:28,276
WORK SHE DIED
TRYING TO ACCOMPLISH.

850
01:02:28,345 --> 01:02:30,879
MY MOTHER MAY
STILL BE ALIVE, JAROD.

851
01:02:30,947 --> 01:02:33,481
WHAT IF SHE'S NOT?

852
01:02:35,085 --> 01:02:37,718
YOU CAN STOP RAINES.

853
01:02:37,787 --> 01:02:40,655
I DON'T KNOW!

854
01:02:40,724 --> 01:02:43,224
OW!

855
01:02:43,293 --> 01:02:47,028
TRUST YOUR INNER SENSE,
MISS PARKER.

856
01:02:51,034 --> 01:02:53,467
I DO.

857
01:02:57,707 --> 01:02:59,541
NOW,

858
01:02:59,609 --> 01:03:01,742
I'M GOING TO FIND MY--

859
01:03:03,614 --> 01:03:06,815
<i> OUR</i> BROTHER.

860
01:03:29,673 --> 01:03:31,806
HAVE I EVER TOLD YOU...

861
01:03:31,875 --> 01:03:35,409
HOW TRULY INSPIRED
THIS HOLY ROLLER
GAG OF YOURS HAS BEEN?

862
01:03:35,478 --> 01:03:37,945
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

863
01:03:38,014 --> 01:03:41,015
OH, COME ON.
YOU'RE ABOUT AS BORN-AGAIN
AS I AM.

864
01:03:42,752 --> 01:03:45,887
BUT, HEY,
AFTER YOU BOTCHED THINGS
SO BADLY LAST YEAR,

865
01:03:45,956 --> 01:03:48,623
THIS RELIGION THING
SAVED YOUR ASS.

866
01:03:48,691 --> 01:03:50,625
THERE'S NO SHAME IN THAT.
OF COURSE,

867
01:03:50,693 --> 01:03:54,095
THE WAY THE TRIUMVIRATE'S
BEEN TOUTING YOU LATELY,
WHO NEEDS DIVINE INTERVENTION?

868
01:03:54,164 --> 01:03:57,699
- YOU'RE MAKING NO SENSE.
- OH, I AM.

869
01:03:57,767 --> 01:04:01,302
JUST AS MUCH AS THIS COMMUNIQUÉ
THAT I INTERCEPTED
FROM THE TRIUMVIRATE DOES.

870
01:04:05,108 --> 01:04:08,209
YOU'VE GOTTEN PRETTY TIGHT
WITH OUR BOSSES IN AFRICA.

871
01:04:08,278 --> 01:04:11,112
<i> 7677 AND MIRAGE.</i>

872
01:04:11,180 --> 01:04:14,949
YOUR POWER PLAY.
RINGIN' A BELL?

873
01:04:15,018 --> 01:04:17,886
HOW DID YOU GET THIS?

874
01:04:17,954 --> 01:04:21,488
<i>IF YOU CAN FIND GOD,</i>
<i>I CAN SURE AS HELL FIND THAT.</i>

875
01:04:21,557 --> 01:04:26,094
<i> AND TO THINK ALL THIS TIME,</i>
<i> I THOUGHT BOBBY BOWMAN...</i>

876
01:04:26,163 --> 01:04:28,496
WAS YOUR ONLY SPECIAL
PROJECT ON THE OUTSIDE.

877
01:04:28,565 --> 01:04:30,731
I GUESS YOU NEVER
HEARD OF PROGRESS.

878
01:04:30,800 --> 01:04:33,567
WHAT I'M ABOUT TO PROPOSE
IS ALL ABOUT PROGRESS.

879
01:04:33,636 --> 01:04:38,306
- WHAT DO YOU WANT?
- I WANT TO RUN THE CENTRE
WITH YOU.

880
01:04:38,375 --> 01:04:41,275
<i> THE 7677 BOMBING</i>
<i> GOES DOWN,</i>

881
01:04:41,344 --> 01:04:44,278
MIRAGE--
OR IS IT ETHAN--

882
01:04:44,347 --> 01:04:47,348
<i> COMES INTO THE CENTRE</i>
<i> JUST LIKE YOU PROMISED</i>
<i> THE TRIUMVIRATE,</i>

883
01:04:47,416 --> 01:04:49,284
AND IT ALL CAN HAPPEN
BECAUSE I DECIDE...

884
01:04:49,352 --> 01:04:53,288
NOT TO TELL MR. PARKER
THAT YOU STOLE HIS SON.

885
01:04:55,391 --> 01:05:00,528
YEAH. THAT YOU STOLE
HIS PRIZED PROJECT MIRAGE.

886
01:05:00,596 --> 01:05:04,299
NOW, IF I READ
THAT COMMUNIQUÉ CORRECTLY,

887
01:05:04,367 --> 01:05:06,801
IT'S ABOUT TIME FOR YOU
TO ACTIVATE ETHAN...

888
01:05:06,870 --> 01:05:11,206
AND FINISH 7677.

889
01:05:11,274 --> 01:05:13,108
WHAT DO YOU SAY, PARTNER?

890
01:05:19,216 --> 01:05:22,383
[ Ringing ]

891
01:05:26,689 --> 01:05:30,624
[ Raines ]
7677 IS A GO.

892
01:05:30,693 --> 01:05:35,496
THIS IS YOUR FINAL CALL.
AFTER THIS, IT'S UP TO YOU.

893
01:05:35,564 --> 01:05:39,467
<i> NOW, WALK THREE BLOCKS</i>
<i> TO THE BUS STATION.</i>

894
01:05:39,536 --> 01:05:41,702
<i> OPEN LOCKER NUMBER 9,</i>

895
01:05:41,771 --> 01:05:46,274
AND YOU'LL FIND
THE FINAL INSTRUCTIONS
FOR THE BOMBING.

896
01:05:49,712 --> 01:05:51,946
<i>[ Voices Whispering ]</i>

897
01:06:04,160 --> 01:06:08,663
<i> WE COULDN'T STOP HIM NOW</i>
<i> EVEN IF WE WANTED TO.</i>

898
01:06:08,731 --> 01:06:11,098
HAPPY?

899
01:06:11,167 --> 01:06:13,434
-<i> [ Door Opens ]</i>
- DAMN HAPPY.

900
01:06:15,805 --> 01:06:17,839
YOU SON OF A--
<i> HEY, HEY.</i>

901
01:06:17,907 --> 01:06:20,108
IS THAT ANY WAY
TO TALK TO YOUR NEW PARTNER?

902
01:06:20,176 --> 01:06:23,010
WHOOPS.
I MEAN, NEW BOSS?

903
01:06:24,447 --> 01:06:26,447
<i>[ Man ]</i>
<i>WE HAVE A CLEAN TRACE</i>
<i>ON THE CALL.</i>

904
01:06:26,515 --> 01:06:30,618
WE'LL MONITOR ETHAN
UNTIL HE FINISHES 7677,
AND THEN WE'LL BRING HIM IN.

905
01:06:30,687 --> 01:06:34,689
- NO SCREW-UPS.
- LOCK HIM UP DOWN IN SL 25...

906
01:06:34,758 --> 01:06:36,857
<i>WITH THE RATS.</i>

907
01:06:44,133 --> 01:06:47,768
WE'VE HAD TOO MANY YEARS
AND TOO MUCH SUCCESS
FOR THINGS TO END THIS WAY.

908
01:06:47,837 --> 01:06:50,137
WHO SAID IT'S ENDING FOR ME?

909
01:06:55,111 --> 01:06:58,379
<i>♪ YOU GOT A SMILE SO BRIGHT ♪</i>

910
01:06:58,448 --> 01:07:01,783
<i>♪ YOU KNOW, YOU COULD</i>
<i>  HAVE BEEN A CANDLE ♪</i>
♪♪ [ Singing Along ]

911
01:07:03,253 --> 01:07:06,987
<i>♪ I'M HOLDING YOU SO TIGHT ♪</i>

912
01:07:07,056 --> 01:07:10,758
<i>♪ YOU KNOW, YOU COULD</i>
<i>  HAVE BEEN A HANDLE ♪</i>

913
01:07:10,827 --> 01:07:14,895
<i>♪ THE WAY YOU SWEPT ME</i>
<i>  OFF ME FEET ♪</i>

914
01:07:14,964 --> 01:07:18,632
<i>♪ YOU KNOW, YOU COULD</i>
<i>  HAVE BEEN A BROOM ♪</i>

915
01:07:18,701 --> 01:07:21,469
<i>♪♪ [ Continues ]</i>
EXCUSE ME?

916
01:07:21,538 --> 01:07:25,406
HI. ANYTHING
I CAN DO TO HELP?

917
01:07:29,913 --> 01:07:31,913
AS A MATTER OF FACT, THERE IS.

918
01:07:31,982 --> 01:07:34,382
<i>♪ AND I CAN TELL ♪</i>

919
01:07:34,451 --> 01:07:36,351
<i>♪ THE WAY YOU DO</i>
<i>   THE THINGS YOU DO ♪♪</i>

920
01:07:38,821 --> 01:07:41,256
<i>[ Bells Tolling ]</i>

921
01:08:12,522 --> 01:08:15,189
HI.
HI.

922
01:08:15,258 --> 01:08:17,758
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?
BETTER.

923
01:08:19,762 --> 01:08:24,165
WE HAVE SO MUCH
WE HAVE TO CATCH UP ON.
I'M GOING TO FIND MOM,

924
01:08:24,233 --> 01:08:28,936
AND WE'RE ALL GOING TO BE
TOGETHER LIKE ONE BIG FAMILY.

925
01:08:29,005 --> 01:08:33,007
AND WHAT ABOUT ETHAN?
DAD TOLD ME EVERYTHING.

926
01:08:33,075 --> 01:08:34,943
HE'S NOT CRAZY,

927
01:08:35,011 --> 01:08:37,011
NOT LIKE YOU THOUGHT HE WAS.

928
01:08:38,281 --> 01:08:42,951
OUR BROTHER, HE'S GIFTED.

929
01:08:43,019 --> 01:08:44,953
HE'S SPECIAL.

930
01:08:45,021 --> 01:08:50,291
DON'T LET THEM DESTROY ETHAN
LIKE THEY DID OUR FAMILY.

931
01:08:50,360 --> 01:08:52,159
I WON'T.

932
01:08:56,166 --> 01:08:58,966
I PROMISE.

933
01:09:08,644 --> 01:09:10,878
SWEET DREAMS.

934
01:09:20,890 --> 01:09:22,890
WHY THE GLUM LOOKS?

935
01:09:24,427 --> 01:09:28,228
WELL, I RECOVERED MORE OF
THE FOREST HOUSE ARCHIVES.

936
01:09:28,298 --> 01:09:30,832
AND?
SIT DOWN, PARKER.

937
01:09:37,806 --> 01:09:40,073
[ Raines ]
I CAN SEE THE HEAD, CATHERINE.

938
01:09:40,142 --> 01:09:42,176
[ Groaning ]

939
01:09:42,244 --> 01:09:43,744
IT'S A--
[ Mrs. Parker ]
BOY.

940
01:09:43,812 --> 01:09:48,048
<i> [ Raines ]</i>
<i> YOU'RE RIGHT.</i>
<i> IT IS A BOY.</i>

941
01:09:50,453 --> 01:09:52,719
OH!

942
01:09:52,788 --> 01:09:56,590
HELLO, ETHAN.

943
01:09:56,659 --> 01:09:59,393
HELLO.
I'M YOUR MOTHER.

944
01:09:59,462 --> 01:10:02,997
I HAVE SUCH
BIG PLANS FOR YOU.

945
01:10:04,633 --> 01:10:08,769
- WHY DIDN'T YOU WANT ME
TO SEE THIS?
- THERE'S MORE, I'M AFRAID.

946
01:10:08,837 --> 01:10:14,408
<i> AFTER MY WORK WAS THROUGH,</i>
<i> I WANTED TO RAISE YOU AND</i>
<i> YOUR BROTHER AND SISTER...</i>

947
01:10:14,477 --> 01:10:17,178
LIKE A REAL FAMILY.

948
01:10:18,547 --> 01:10:21,983
BUT I'M NOT GONNA BE ABLE
TO DO THAT, LITTLE MAN.

949
01:10:30,926 --> 01:10:35,562
I JUST REALIZED
I'M NOT GOING TO BE ABLE
TO SEE YOU GROW UP.

950
01:10:37,233 --> 01:10:41,636
BUT YOU HAVE A BROTHER
AND SISTER THAT WILL
FIND YOU AND PROTECT YOU.

951
01:10:41,705 --> 01:10:44,806
YOU TELL THEM
TO FINISH MY WORK,

952
01:10:44,874 --> 01:10:47,175
TO FINISH MY PLAN.

953
01:10:50,013 --> 01:10:51,946
I LOVE YOU.

954
01:11:02,491 --> 01:11:04,492
[ Crying ]

955
01:11:07,530 --> 01:11:10,264
UM, I DON'T THINK
YOU NEED TO SEE--
NO.

956
01:11:10,333 --> 01:11:12,333
I NEED TO KNOW.

957
01:11:19,976 --> 01:11:23,010
I'M SORRY.
I'M JUST FOLLOWING ORDERS.

958
01:11:23,078 --> 01:11:25,913
<i> [ Mrs. Parker ]</i>
<i> YOU REALLY HAD ME CONVINCED</i>
<i> THAT YOU HAD CHANGED,</i>

959
01:11:25,981 --> 01:11:28,316
THAT YOU CARED ABOUT
THIS BABY.

960
01:11:28,385 --> 01:11:30,284
THERE'S NO OTHER WAY, CATHERINE.

961
01:11:30,353 --> 01:11:32,453
<i> [ Gunshot ]</i>

962
01:11:35,425 --> 01:11:39,160
RAINES JUST EXECUTED HER.

963
01:11:40,396 --> 01:11:43,064
<i> [ Baby Crying ]</i>

964
01:11:48,504 --> 01:11:51,372
HAVE HER CREMATED.
YES, DOCTOR.

965
01:11:55,911 --> 01:11:58,345
I'M YOUR MOMMY NOW.

966
01:12:28,311 --> 01:12:32,880
RAINES EXECUTED MY MOTHER.
HE WON'T TAKE MY BROTHER TOO.

967
01:12:38,120 --> 01:12:40,821
SYD, TALK TO HER.

968
01:12:43,192 --> 01:12:45,359
THERE'S NOTHING LEFT
TO SAY.

969
01:12:46,763 --> 01:12:49,764
<i>[ Major Charles ]</i>
<i>YOU FOUND ETHAN'S COMPUTER?</i>

970
01:12:49,832 --> 01:12:52,499
<i> AT THE WAREHOUSE</i>
<i> WHERE HE PICKED UP</i>
<i> THE BOMB COMPONENTS.</i>

971
01:12:52,568 --> 01:12:56,103
<i>I RECONSTRUCTED THE HARD DRIVE</i>
<i>AND WAS ABLE TO BREAK DOWN</i>
<i>THE BOMB SCHEMATIC.</i>

972
01:12:56,171 --> 01:12:59,239
<i>BUT EVEN BETTER,</i>
<i>I FOUND OUT WHERE</i>
<i>THE BOMBING IS GOING DOWN.</i>

973
01:12:59,308 --> 01:13:02,275
<i> 7677. IT'S THE NUMBER</i>
<i> OF A SUBWAY TRAIN.</i>

974
01:13:02,344 --> 01:13:06,280
D.C. UNDERGROUND.
THE SUBWAY'S
NOT HIS TARGET.

975
01:13:06,349 --> 01:13:08,916
IT'S HIS DELIVERY SYSTEM.

976
01:13:08,985 --> 01:13:12,553
<i>TRAIN 7677'S ROUTE</i>
<i>ENDS AT FREEDOM STATION.</i>

977
01:13:12,622 --> 01:13:15,189
<i>DIRECTLY ABOVE THAT</i>
<i>IS THE NATIONAL HOTEL.</i>

978
01:13:15,258 --> 01:13:19,260
THE EXACT PLACE WHERE HUNDREDS
OF FOREIGN DIGNITARIES ARE
STAYING FOR A PEACE CONFERENCE.

979
01:13:19,328 --> 01:13:21,262
SO MUCH FOR PEACE.

980
01:13:21,330 --> 01:13:23,931
I BROKE DOWN THE PASSWORD
ON A WELL-HIDDEN
ENCRYPTION FILE.

981
01:13:24,000 --> 01:13:26,600
ETHAN'S PROGRAMMED
THE BOMB'S TIMER
ON THIS LAPTOP TOO.

982
01:13:26,669 --> 01:13:29,203
THE TRAIN IS LEAVING THE STATION
IN EXACTLY ONE HOUR FROM NOW.

983
01:13:29,271 --> 01:13:32,239
- IT'S JUST ENOUGH TIME
TO STOP THIS AND SAVE ETHAN.
- COME ON.

984
01:13:35,311 --> 01:13:37,711
<i>[ Ringing ]</i>
<i>[ Electronic Voice ]</i>
<i>YOU HAVE A VIDEO PHONE CALL.</i>

985
01:13:42,619 --> 01:13:46,721
I'M SORRY TO CALL SO LATE,
JAROD, BUT I THOUGHT
FOR SURE YOU'D BE INTERESTED...

986
01:13:46,789 --> 01:13:49,055
IN SAVING THE LIFE
OF A CLOSE FRIEND.

987
01:13:49,124 --> 01:13:50,724
[ Groans ]
OUCH!

988
01:13:50,793 --> 01:13:52,058
- ZOE!
- JAROD!

989
01:13:52,127 --> 01:13:55,463
- LYLE, LET HER GO!
- THAT'S EXACTLY
WHAT I WANNA DO.

990
01:13:55,531 --> 01:13:59,900
BUT MR. COX ACTUALLY
WANTS TO EXPLOIT THE SAFETY AND
WELL-BEING OF YOUR GIRLFRIEND...

991
01:13:59,969 --> 01:14:01,836
TO HIS ADVANTAGE.

992
01:14:01,904 --> 01:14:03,671
ALL RIGHT.
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

993
01:14:03,740 --> 01:14:05,906
TO PROPOSE A QUID PRO QUO.

994
01:14:05,975 --> 01:14:08,809
DON'T, JAROD!
I DON'T KNOW WHY
THESE PEOPLE WANT YOU,

995
01:14:08,878 --> 01:14:11,145
BUT THEY WILL KILL YOU,
I KNOW THAT!

996
01:14:11,214 --> 01:14:13,113
<i>[ Mr. Cox ]</i>
<i>IF YOU WANT ZOE TO LIVE,</i>

997
01:14:13,182 --> 01:14:15,816
<i>YOU'LL SURRENDER YOURSELF TO US</i>
<i>TONIGHT AT ROSING'S FARM,</i>

998
01:14:15,885 --> 01:14:18,252
HIGHWAY 12,
OUTSIDE BLUE COVE...

999
01:14:18,320 --> 01:14:20,988
IN EXACTLY ONE HOUR.

1000
01:14:22,658 --> 01:14:25,292
LYLE! DAMN IT!

1001
01:14:25,361 --> 01:14:30,964
ONE HOUR FROM NOW.
THAT'S EXACTLY WHEN ETHAN
WILL BE ON THAT SUBWAY TRAIN.

1002
01:14:43,779 --> 01:14:46,046
<i>[ Rats Squealing ]</i>

1003
01:15:04,033 --> 01:15:09,404
MY FIRST MEMORY OF YOU
WAS IN THE CENTRE LOBBY.

1004
01:15:09,472 --> 01:15:11,405
YOU WERE SMOKING A CIGARETTE.

1005
01:15:11,474 --> 01:15:17,111
I WAS SIX OR SEVEN,
AND YOU KNELT DOWN,

1006
01:15:17,180 --> 01:15:21,048
TOOK A DRAG
AND BLEW SMOKE IN MY FACE.

1007
01:15:21,117 --> 01:15:23,485
<i>AND HERE YOU ARE...</i>

1008
01:15:25,121 --> 01:15:29,690
STILL BLOWIN' SMOKE.

1009
01:15:34,097 --> 01:15:36,764
FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH,
MISS PARKER--

1010
01:15:36,833 --> 01:15:40,234
I CAN NEVER HAVE MY MOTHER BACK,

1011
01:15:40,303 --> 01:15:43,371
BUT I CAN DAMN WELL
SAVE MY BROTHER.

1012
01:15:43,439 --> 01:15:48,475
<i>YOU TELL ME EVERYTHING YOU KNOW</i>
<i>ABOUT 7677,</i>

1013
01:15:48,544 --> 01:15:51,746
AND I CONSIDER
LETTING YOU LIVE ANOTHER DAY.

1014
01:15:54,517 --> 01:15:57,885
I'M THE LAST CHANCE SALOON HERE,
RAINES.

1015
01:15:59,689 --> 01:16:04,992
7677 IS A WASHINGTON D.C.
SUBWAY TRAIN...

1016
01:16:05,061 --> 01:16:09,764
DEPARTING FROM BEACON STATION
IN A LITTLE OVER
ONE HOUR FROM NOW.

1017
01:16:09,833 --> 01:16:12,232
THEN WHAT?

1018
01:16:12,302 --> 01:16:14,234
WHEN IT PULLS INTO
FREEDOM STATION,

1019
01:16:14,304 --> 01:16:16,304
THE SUBWAY AND EVERYTHING
ABOVE IT WILL BLOW UP.

1020
01:16:21,244 --> 01:16:25,145
IT'S YOUR BROTHER WHO WILL PLANT
THE BOMB AND GUIDE THE SUBWAY.

1021
01:16:28,217 --> 01:16:31,553
OUR FATHER,
WHO ART IN HEAVEN--
NOT SO FAST.

1022
01:16:31,621 --> 01:16:35,790
<i>BEFORE SHE DIED,</i>
<i>MY MOTHER SAID SOMETHING</i>
<i>ABOUT HER "UNFINISHED WORK,"</i>

1023
01:16:35,859 --> 01:16:37,725
<i>ABOUT HER "PLAN."</i>

1024
01:16:37,793 --> 01:16:39,593
WHAT DID SHE MEAN BY THAT?

1025
01:16:42,131 --> 01:16:45,633
- THEN YOU NEVER
FOUND IT EITHER?
- FOUND WHAT?

1026
01:16:45,701 --> 01:16:50,471
WORD HAS IT YOUR MOTHER
LEFT A D.S.A. EXPLAINING
EXACTLY WHAT HER PLAN WAS.

1027
01:16:50,540 --> 01:16:53,708
<i>BUT IT WAS THE ONE PIECE</i>
<i>OF INCRIMINATING EVIDENCE...</i>

1028
01:16:53,777 --> 01:16:56,544
I NEVER FOUND OR DESTROYED.

1029
01:16:56,613 --> 01:16:59,780
YOU FIND IT,
YOU FIND HER PLAN.

1030
01:17:03,420 --> 01:17:06,086
YOU GOTTA KNOW
SOMETHING MORE ABOUT IT.

1031
01:17:06,155 --> 01:17:08,856
IT'S ABOUT WHAT
EVERYTHING'S ABOUT,
MISS PARKER.

1032
01:17:08,925 --> 01:17:13,327
IT'S ABOUT THE CENTRE,
ALL THE LIES.

1033
01:17:14,764 --> 01:17:16,930
<i>JUST REMEMBER,</i>

1034
01:17:16,999 --> 01:17:18,966
WHATEVER ANSWERS YOUR MOTHER
MAY HAVE LEFT BEHIND,

1035
01:17:19,035 --> 01:17:23,170
<i> THERE IS STILL</i>
<i> ONE PERSON ALIVE...</i>

1036
01:17:23,239 --> 01:17:25,206
WHO DOES KNOW THE WHOLE TRUTH.

1037
01:17:26,842 --> 01:17:29,309
<i> WHO?</i>
<i>[ Gunshot ]</i>

1038
01:17:35,518 --> 01:17:37,885
[ Sighs ]
DADDY?

1039
01:17:37,953 --> 01:17:41,722
IT'S NOT RIGHT FOR
MY LITTLE GIRL TO HAVE
BLOOD LIKE THAT ON HER HANDS.

1040
01:17:44,560 --> 01:17:47,494
WAS IT THE BLOOD
YOU WERE WORRIED ABOUT,

1041
01:17:47,563 --> 01:17:50,865
OR THE TRUTH?

1042
01:18:02,645 --> 01:18:05,246
JAROD SHOULD BE HERE
IN 20 MINUTES.

1043
01:18:05,314 --> 01:18:07,981
TAKE YOUR POSITIONS.
BE READY.

1044
01:18:08,050 --> 01:18:10,517
[ Mr. Lyle ]
AND YOU'RE SURE HE'LL COME?

1045
01:18:10,586 --> 01:18:12,987
OH, HE'LL COME.

1046
01:18:45,988 --> 01:18:48,689
ZOE, WE COULDN'T HAVE
DONE THIS WITHOUT YOU.

1047
01:18:48,758 --> 01:18:52,093
<i> GO TO HELL.</i>
ALL'S FAIR
IN LOVE AND WAR.

1048
01:18:52,161 --> 01:18:54,195
YOU KNOW, IT'S TOO BAD
YOU'RE NOT ASIAN.

1049
01:18:54,264 --> 01:18:57,364
BUT MAYBE WHEN ALL THIS IS OVER,
WE CAN FIND A PLACE FOR YOU
IN OUR RENEWAL WING.

1050
01:19:00,436 --> 01:19:03,704
-<i> WHY CAN'T YOU JUST</i>
<i>  LEAVE JAROD ALONE?</i>
- BECAUSE HE BELONGS TO US.

1051
01:19:22,458 --> 01:19:24,592
[ Screams ]

1052
01:19:26,996 --> 01:19:29,163
[ Coughing ]

1053
01:19:46,749 --> 01:19:49,583
IT'S NOT JAROD!
IT'S MAJOR CHARLES.

1054
01:20:22,151 --> 01:20:24,618
<i> [ Cell Phone Ringing ]</i>

1055
01:20:26,022 --> 01:20:28,122
DAD?
IT'S ME-- ZOE.

1056
01:20:28,191 --> 01:20:31,158
- THEN YOU'RE ALL RIGHT?
- YEAH, EVERYTHING'S OKAY
ON THIS END, JAROD.

1057
01:20:31,227 --> 01:20:34,895
THOUGH I AM PRETTY DAMN CURIOUS
ABOUT WHO COX AND LYLE ARE.

1058
01:20:34,964 --> 01:20:37,898
- I AM SO SORRY THAT
YOU GOT INVOLVED WITH THIS.
- BE CAREFUL, JAROD.

1059
01:20:37,967 --> 01:20:39,700
I WILL.

1060
01:22:24,140 --> 01:22:26,073
<i> ETHAN?</i>

1061
01:22:26,142 --> 01:22:29,409
- STAY AWAY!
- I'M NOT GOING TO HURT YOU.

1062
01:22:29,478 --> 01:22:31,978
<i>[ Voices Whispering ]</i>
[ Grunting ]

1063
01:22:32,047 --> 01:22:34,314
THEY SAY NOT TO TRUST YOU.
<i>NO, THEY DON'T.</i>

1064
01:22:34,383 --> 01:22:37,184
- NOT ALL OF THEM.
- I WISH I DIDN'T HAVE
TO HEAR THEM!

1065
01:22:37,253 --> 01:22:41,622
IT'S YOUR INNER SENSE, ETHAN.

1066
01:22:41,691 --> 01:22:45,359
IT'S WHAT MAKES YOU SPECIAL.

1067
01:22:45,428 --> 01:22:48,362
- WHO ARE YOU?
- I'M YOUR BROTHER.

1068
01:22:51,167 --> 01:22:53,367
- SHE TOLD ME ABOUT YOU.
- SHE?

1069
01:22:54,537 --> 01:22:56,937
OF COURSE.

1070
01:22:57,006 --> 01:23:00,607
ONE OF THE VOICES.
SHE'S THE ONE
YOU MUST LISTEN TO, ETHAN.

1071
01:23:01,944 --> 01:23:04,444
- WHO IS SHE?
- YOUR MOTHER.

1072
01:23:04,513 --> 01:23:08,348
<i> YOU NEVER GOT TO KNOW HER.</i>
<i> THEY NEVER ALLOWED YOU</i>
<i> TO KNOW HER.</i>

1073
01:23:08,417 --> 01:23:12,319
BUT SHE IS YOUR MOTHER.
SHE'S YOUR GUIDE, ETHAN.

1074
01:23:12,387 --> 01:23:14,388
LISTEN TO HER VOICE.
IT'S YOUR INNER SENSE.

1075
01:23:14,456 --> 01:23:19,793
- MR. RAINES IS MY GUIDE.
- NO, HE TOOK YOUR GIFTS
AND HE USED THEM AGAINST YOU.

1076
01:23:19,862 --> 01:23:23,831
HE TAUGHT YOU TO FEAR
THOSE VOICES INSTEAD OF
LEARNING HOW TO EMBRACE THEM.

1077
01:23:23,900 --> 01:23:27,168
<i> HE USED YOU, ETHAN.</i>
<i> HE'S STILL USING YOU.</i>

1078
01:23:27,236 --> 01:23:29,870
DON'T LET HIM USE
YOUR GIFT FOR DESTRUCTION.

1079
01:23:29,939 --> 01:23:35,342
- I HAVE TO FOLLOW HIS WORD.
- IF YOU DO, THEN
INNOCENT PEOPLE WILL DIE.

1080
01:23:35,411 --> 01:23:38,079
THAT'S NOT YOU, ETHAN.
THAT'S NOT WHO YOU ARE.

1081
01:23:38,147 --> 01:23:42,082
<i>JUST LISTEN TO HER VOICE, ETHAN.</i>
<i>FOCUS ON HER VOICE.</i>

1082
01:23:50,259 --> 01:23:54,762
TRUST HIM, SON.
JAROD IS THE ONE.

1083
01:23:59,135 --> 01:24:00,867
LISTEN TO HER.

1084
01:24:09,145 --> 01:24:15,082
♪ CREE CRAW TOAD'S FOOT ♪

1085
01:24:15,151 --> 01:24:18,352
[ Together ]
♪ GEESE WALK BAREFOOT ♪

1086
01:24:18,421 --> 01:24:23,290
- ♪ CREE CRAW TOAD'S FOOT
GEESE WALK BAREFOOT ♪
- BROTHER?

1087
01:24:23,358 --> 01:24:29,096
YES.
♪ CREE CRAW TOAD'S FOOT
GEESE WALK BAREFOOT ♪♪

1088
01:24:29,165 --> 01:24:32,600
YOU CAN BREAK FREE OF THE HOLD
HE HAS OVER YOU.
JUST LISTEN TO HER VOICE.

1089
01:24:32,668 --> 01:24:37,871
YOU HAVE A FAMILY NOW,
A REAL FAMILY.
WE'LL ALWAYS BE THERE.

1090
01:24:39,442 --> 01:24:41,709
NOW TELL ME,
WHERE IS THE BOMB?

1091
01:24:49,318 --> 01:24:52,286
<i>YOU CAN'T STOP THE TRAIN.</i>
<i>THE BOMB CAN'T BE DEFUSED.</i>

1092
01:24:52,355 --> 01:24:55,555
I WAS ON THREE BOMB SQUADS
AND TWO ARMY DEMOLITION UNITS.
I CAN DEFUSE IT.

1093
01:24:55,624 --> 01:24:58,592
<i>THE BOMB'S ON THE UNDERCARRIAGE.</i>
<i>THERE'S NO STOPPING IT</i>
<i>OR THE TRAIN.</i>

1094
01:24:58,661 --> 01:25:01,428
<i>THEN WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO SEND</i>
<i>THE TRAIN SOMEWHERE ELSE.</i>
<i>WHERE'S FREEDOM STATION?</i>

1095
01:25:01,496 --> 01:25:04,098
<i>IT'S ON THE TRACK VEERING RIGHT.</i>
<i> WHERE'S THE TRACK</i>
<i> VEERING LEFT GO?</i>

1096
01:25:04,167 --> 01:25:06,167
<i>IT'S TO AN ABANDONED</i>
<i>MAINTENANCE YARD.</i>
<i>THEY CLOSED IT YEARS AGO.</i>

1097
01:25:06,235 --> 01:25:08,134
WELL, HANG ON.
<i>LOOK, IT'S NO USE.</i>

1098
01:25:08,203 --> 01:25:10,403
<i>I PROGRAMMED IT</i>
<i>TO AUTOMATICALLY TAKE</i>
<i>THE TRACK TO THE RIGHT.</i>

1099
01:25:10,472 --> 01:25:13,673
- DID I TELL YOU I WAS
A ROCKET SCIENTIST TOO?
-<i> 3,000 YARDS.</i>

1100
01:25:15,912 --> 01:25:18,779
-<i> 2,900.</i>
- COME ON!

1101
01:25:18,847 --> 01:25:21,581
<i>2,800! DO IT!</i>

1102
01:25:25,654 --> 01:25:28,421
- I GOT IT.
- THE TRAIN HAS AN AUTO BRAKE
THAT ENGAGES IN 40 SECONDS.

1103
01:25:28,490 --> 01:25:31,825
-<i> THE BOMB GOES OFF</i>
<i> 20 SECONDS AFTER THAT.</i>
- COME ON! GET OUT OF HERE!

1104
01:25:40,403 --> 01:25:43,270
FREEZE IT, PLEASE!

1105
01:25:45,775 --> 01:25:48,808
- MISS PARKER, LISTEN TO ME.
THERE IS A BOMB ON BOARD.
-<i> I KNOW!</i>

1106
01:25:48,877 --> 01:25:51,145
<i>WE HAVE LESS THAN 60 SECONDS.</i>
THEN DEFUSE IT!

1107
01:25:51,213 --> 01:25:53,046
<i>I CAN'T!</i>
<i>IT'S UNDERNEATH THE TRAIN!</i>

1108
01:25:53,115 --> 01:25:55,782
- THEN STOP THE TRAIN!
- IT'S TOO LATE!

1109
01:25:55,851 --> 01:25:58,518
<i>IF WE ARE LUCKY,</i>
<i>THIS TRAIN WILL SLOW DOWN ENOUGH</i>
<i>FOR US TO JUMP OFF.</i>

1110
01:25:58,588 --> 01:26:01,155
BUT I CAN'T STOP THE EXPLOSION.

1111
01:26:01,223 --> 01:26:03,557
<i>THIS IS YOUR BROTHER,</i>
<i>MISS PARKER. OUR BROTHER.</i>

1112
01:26:03,626 --> 01:26:07,461
<i>IT COULD BE A BEGINNING.</i>
<i>DON'T MAKE IT AN END!</i>

1113
01:26:07,529 --> 01:26:10,998
<i>[ Mrs. Parker's Voice ]</i>
<i>I'M YOUR MOTHER.</i>
<i>I LOVE YOU.</i>

1114
01:26:11,066 --> 01:26:13,467
YOU SOUND JUST LIKE HER.

1115
01:26:16,272 --> 01:26:19,373
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>IT'S YOUR MOTHER'S VOICE</i>
<i>HE CAN HEAR, MISS PARKER.</i>

1116
01:26:19,442 --> 01:26:24,211
<i>MAYBE YOU CAN HEAR IT TOO.</i>
<i>TRUST THAT VOICE.</i>

1117
01:26:25,548 --> 01:26:29,149
MISS PARKER?

1118
01:26:29,218 --> 01:26:32,686
<i>THE AUTO BRAKE HAS ENGAGED.</i>
<i>WE HAVE LESS THAN 20 SECONDS.</i>

1119
01:26:32,754 --> 01:26:34,588
- [ Groans ]
- WHAT'S THE MATTER WITH HIM?

1120
01:26:34,657 --> 01:26:38,358
SIDE EFFECTS OF RAINES'S WORK.
NOW WHAT'S IT GONNA BE,
MISS PARKER?

1121
01:26:38,427 --> 01:26:42,229
<i>HELP ME SAVE HIM.</i>
<i> HELP ME SAVE OUR FAMILY.</i>

1122
01:26:42,298 --> 01:26:45,532
IT'S YOUR CHOICE.

1123
01:26:46,836 --> 01:26:49,536
COME ON.
PUT YOUR ARM AROUND ME.

1124
01:27:20,436 --> 01:27:22,436
GO!

1125
01:27:24,206 --> 01:27:25,973
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>NOW WHAT?</i>
<i> [ Jarod ] WE JUMP!</i>

1126
01:27:26,041 --> 01:27:28,308
NOW!

1127
01:27:51,833 --> 01:27:54,435
<i>[ Car Alarms Blaring ]</i>

